NK105(be)001:1252: rgyud ni bya spyod rnal 'byor thub pa rgyud //
NK105(be)001:1253: thabs shes gnyis med pha ma gnyis su med //
NK105(be)001:1254: nang pa sngags te rnal 'byor chen po'o //
NK105(be)001:1255: de yi yi ge glegs bam la sogs yin //
NK105(be)001:1256: rtogs pa'i chos kyi sa lam bskyed rdzogs te //
NK105(be)001:1257: gzungs dang ting 'dzin ye shes snying po can //
NK105(be)001:1258: thugs rje'i rang bzhin thabs tshul dpag med do //
NK105(be)001:1259: de yang rab dga' dri med 'od byed pa //
NK105(be)001:1260: 'od 'phro sbyang dka' mngon gyur ring du song //
NK105(be)001:1261: mi g.yo legs pa'i blo gros chos kyi sprin //
NK105(be)001:1262: slob pa'i sa bcu bcu gcig kun du 'od //
NK105(be)001:1263: sprul sku'i sa ste rgyu yi theg pas bzhag /
NK105(be)001:1264: rdo rje'i theg par yon tan rigs dbye bas //
NK105(be)001:1265: bcu gnyis la sogs rnam gzhag dpag tu med //
NK105(be)001:1266: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob lam lnga dang //
NK105(be)001:1267: rim gnyis la sogs zab mo sems kyi yul //
NK105(be)001:1268: dam chos nyi ma dri med 'od manga'o //
NK105(be)001:1269: dge 'dun nyan rang skyes bu zung bzhi dang //
NK105(be)001:1270: rgyal sras sar gnas phyi ste mkha' 'gro dang //
NK105(be)001:1271: gsang sngags rjes slob 'gro ba nang du 'dod //
NK105(be)001:1272: 'di dag dmigs pa'i yul te nam mkhar bsam //
NK105(be)001:1273: khyad par bla ma sangs rgyas gtso bor 'dod //
NK105(be)001:1274: rnam pa dngos yid gsang bas rab mchod de //
NK105(be)001:1275: bdag dang 'gro kun gus pas thal sbyar zhing //
NK105(be)001:1276: bla ma sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK105(be)001:1277: byang chub bar du gzhan don skyabs su 'gro //
NK105(be)001:1278: snying khong rus pa'i gting nas yang yang bya //
NK105(be)001:1279: dgyes shing 'od zer bkye bas rang gzhan gyi //
NK105(be)001:1280: sgo gsum sgrib sbyongs dngos grub thob par bsam //
NK105(be)001:1281: de yis bsod nams tshogs rdzogs gzugs sku 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1282: mthar thug 'bras bu'i skyabs gnas chos sku ste //
NK105(be)001:1283: sangs rgyas chos tshogs snying po don gyi lha //
NK105(be)001:1284: rang sems 'od gsal spros kun bral ba yin //
NK105(be)001:1285: de yi lam 'khyer skyabs su 'gro ba ni //
NK105(be)001:1286: rgyu yi thun rjes thams cad rang gi sems //
NK105(be)001:1287: don la 'gro bya 'gro byed gnyis med pas //
NK105(be)001:1288: ji bzhin ngang la de bzhin mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:1289: yul sems gnyis su 'dzin na mthar thug min //
NK105(be)001:1290: 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro smon pa med pa yin //
NK105(be)001:1291: des ni ye shes tshogs rdzogs chos sku 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1292: rjes snang rmi lam sgyu mar bsngo ba bya //
NK105(be)001:1293: bslab bya gnyis las rgyu yi rim pa ni //
NK105(be)001:1294: srog dang rgyal srid bya dga' la sogs phyir //
NK105(be)001:1295: bla ma dang ni dkon mchog spang mi bya //
NK105(be)001:1296: bla mar skyabs song mchod 'os mi slu zhing //
NK105(be)001:1297: dam pa rnams la skur 'debs mi snyan spang //
NK105(be)001:1298: sangs rgyas skyabs song lha gzhan phyag mi btsal //
NK105(be)001:1299: chos la skyabs song sems can 'tshe ba spang //
NK105(be)001:1300: dge 'dun skyabs song mu stegs can mi 'grogs //
NK105(be)001:1301: de dag gzugs la'ang dad pas rab mchod cing //
NK105(be)001:1302: nyin mtshan rjes dran rtag par skyabs su 'gro //
NK105(be)001:1303: 'bras bu'i bslab bya mnyam nyid nan tan bya //
NK105(be)001:1304: bzang ngan mi rtog mchog dman blang dor min //
NK105(be)001:1305: spros la mi brten chos nyid gnyug mar sbyang //
NK105(be)001:1306: thams cad lhun rdzogs dkyil 'khor gcig tu spyad //
NK105(be)001:1307: gtong rgyu btags pa khas len 'das pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1308: mtshan nyid pa ni log lta skyes pas gtong //
NK105(be)001:1309: bslab bya nyams pas dman par ltung ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1310: bag yod dran pas bsgrims te blang dor bya //
NK105(be)001:1311: skyabs gzhan gang gis slu ba de mthong nas //
NK105(be)001:1312: lhag par thugs rje'i lha la dad pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:1313: tshe rabs kun du 'jigs bral skyob pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1314: de las phan bde byed pa gang zhig yod //
NK105(be)001:1315: de na sems gtsang dad pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK105(be)001:1316: bsod nams ye shes char chus legs bran te //
NK105(be)001:1317: chos khams dge ba'i myu gu cher 'phel bas //
NK105(be)001:1318: rgyal ba'i phun tshogs lo thog smin par byed //
NK105(be)001:1319: chos tshul dge ba ngo tsha khrel yod shes //
NK105(be)001:1320: bag yod dran pa yon tan tshogs mang zhing //
NK105(be)001:1321: gzungs sprin ye shes nyi ma sems la 'char //
NK105(be)001:1322: rmi lam na yang mi 'bral mthong ba dang //
NK105(be)001:1323: tshe rabs dran zhing rigs dang 'byor pas mdzes //
NK105(be)001:1324: 'gro kun dga' bas don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:1325: mthar yang rang nyid lus can kun gyi skyabs //
NK105(be)001:1326: dpung gnyen byed pas sku gsum 'byor pa 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:1327: skyabs song yon tan gal te gzugs mchis na //
NK105(be)001:1328: nam mkhas ches lhag bsod nams pha mtha' yas //
NK105(be)001:1329: legs pa'i yon tan kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK105(be)001:1330: de la mkhas pa su zhig brten mi bgyid //
NK105(be)001:1331: nyes spong zhi ba 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen //
NK105(be)001:1332: dad brgya'i spyi bos rab tu phyag 'tshal zhing //
NK105(be)001:1333: sa gsum bsod nams 'dren mchog dpag bsam shing //
NK105(be)001:1334: phan bde'i 'byung gnas de la skyabs su mchi //
NK105(be)001:1335: de ltar bde chen yon tan mchog bsgrags pas //
NK105(be)001:1336: skye dgu dam pa'i spyod la legs gzhol zhing //
NK105(be)001:1337: nyes gyur dman pa'i yul la brten pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1338: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:1339: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:1340: skyabs su 'gro ba'i le'u ste drug pa'o////de ltar skyabs song rten gyi gang zag gis //
NK105(be)001:1341: byams pa'i sa gzhir snying rje'i me tog bkram //
NK105(be)001:1342: dga' ba'i grib bsil btang snyoms chu gtsang gis //
NK105(be)001:1343: 'gro la phan phyir rang gi sems sbyang ngo //
NK105(be)001:1344: de yang thar pa'i lam dang ma 'brel na //
NK105(be)001:1345: tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi ste srid pa'i rgyu //
NK105(be)001:1346: zhi ba'i lam gyis zin pa'i de rnam bzhi //
NK105(be)001:1347: srid pa'i chu gter 'da' phyir tshad med bzhi //
NK105(be)001:1348: dmigs yul mtha' yas 'gro ba chos nyid la //
NK105(be)001:1349: rnam pa kun khyab dmigs bcas dmigs pa med //
NK105(be)001:1350: snga ma tshad yod nyung zad 'gro ba la //
NK105(be)001:1351: dmigs rnams ma dag dmigs bcas tshangs pa'i rgyu //
NK105(be)001:1352: 'di ni dmigs med thar par gzhol bas na //
NK105(be)001:1353: snying rje'i rang bzhin can gyis bslab par bya //
NK105(be)001:1354: bde ba mi ldan sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag /
NK105(be)001:1355: skyid cing 'byor la nye ring chags sdang can //
NK105(be)001:1356: byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms yul //
NK105(be)001:1357: rnam pa bde thob sdug bsngal bral ba dang //
NK105(be)001:1358: dga' dang mi 'bral sems snyoms las rung 'dod //
NK105(be)001:1359: sgom tshul go rims nges pa med na yang //
NK105(be)001:1360: dang po'i gang zag thog mar btang snyoms te //
NK105(be)001:1361: nye ring bsnyams nas de nas gzhan gsum sgom //
NK105(be)001:1362: de yang dmigs yul sems can thams cad la //
NK105(be)001:1363: blo yi rnam pa 'di ltar brtag par bya //
NK105(be)001:1364: da lta pha dang ma dang bshes la chags //
NK105(be)001:1365: dgra la sdang ba 'di 'dra'i sems khyod ngan //
NK105(be)001:1366: thog mtha' dus med 'khyams tshe dgra 'dis kyang //
NK105(be)001:1367: pha ma la sogs bshes byas phan pa bsgrubs //
NK105(be)001:1368: de yi drin lan gnod sems sgom byed dam //
NK105(be)001:1369: gnyen 'dis kyang ni dgra byas gnod pa bsgrubs //
NK105(be)001:1370: da lta na yang de yi sdug bsngal 'go //
NK105(be)001:1371: de yi lan du phan pa ji ltar rigs //
NK105(be)001:1372: bar ma yang ni mdza' dang mi mdzar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1373: phan gnod ma nges chags sdang rigs pa min //
NK105(be)001:1374: de bas thog mar mdza' bshes phyogs rnams la //
NK105(be)001:1375: bar ma bzhin du chags pa spang bya zhing //
NK105(be)001:1376: de nas dgra la bar ma bzhin du ni //
NK105(be)001:1377: sdang ba spangs la nye ring med par bya //
NK105(be)001:1378: bar ma'i phyogs la'ang gti mug dbral ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1379: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs snyam du sel ba'i blo //
NK105(be)001:1380: srid dang bral ba de 'dra rnam par bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1381: thams cad bde 'dod sdug bsngal 'dor 'dod gcig /'on kyang mi shes sdug bsngal rgyu la spyod //
NK105(be)001:1382: kye ma nyam thag 'gro ba'i nyon mongs tshogs //
NK105(be)001:1383: bag chags bcas kun zhi la sems snyoms shog /
NK105(be)001:1384: chags sdang drag pos gzir ba'i lus can kun //
NK105(be)001:1385: nye ring sems snyoms chags sdang bral bar shog /
NK105(be)001:1386: ces bsam 'gro ba gcig nas gnyis dang gsum //
NK105(be)001:1387: yul gru gcig nas gling gcig gling bzhi nas //
NK105(be)001:1388: stong gcig gnyis gsum 'jig rten kun la bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1389: 'byongs pa'i tshad ni bdag gzhan dgra gnyen mnyam //
NK105(be)001:1390: rjes la dmigs pa med pa'i btang snyoms yul //
NK105(be)001:1391: thams cad sems te sems nyid nam mkha' 'dra //
NK105(be)001:1392: don dam ma skyes stong pa'i ngang de la //
NK105(be)001:1393: blo yi rnam pa spros dang bral gzhag /'byongs pa'i tshad ni zab zhi'i rtogs pa skye //
NK105(be)001:1394: 'bras bu nye ring rnyog pa med pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:1395: gnas lugs don la rang bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:1396: de ltar kun la sems snyoms gyur pa na //
NK105(be)001:1397: rang nyid ma la bde dang phrad 'dod ltar //
NK105(be)001:1398: lus can kun la de bzhin bsam par bya //
NK105(be)001:1399: byams pa'i dmigs yul sems can thams cad la //
NK105(be)001:1400: rnam pa gnas skabs lha mi'i bde ba dang //
NK105(be)001:1401: mthar thug byang chub bde dang 'phrad par shog /
NK105(be)001:1402: snyam du gcig nas 'gro ba kun gyi bar //
NK105(be)001:1403: phyogs mtha' gtugs par de snyed bsgom par bya //
NK105(be)001:1404: rtags ni kun la khyab pa'i byams pa mchog /
NK105(be)001:1405: bu gcig brtse ba'i ma bas lhag pa 'byung //
NK105(be)001:1406: de rjes thams cad mnyam pa'i ngang la gzhag /
NK105(be)001:1407: dmigs pa med pa'i byams pa chen po ste //
NK105(be)001:1408: byams dang stong pa zung du chud pa rtags //
NK105(be)001:1409: 'bras bu mthong na yid 'ong dag pa 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1410: byams pas 'gro la khyab pa'i rjes nyid du //
NK105(be)001:1411: pha ma'i sdug bsngal blos mi bzod pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1412: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal bsams la snying rje bskyed //
NK105(be)001:1413: de yang bdag gi pha ma drin can rnams //
NK105(be)001:1414: bdag gi ched du sdig pa'i las byas pas //
NK105(be)001:1415: tsha grang bkres skom gsad gcad las kyis mnar //
NK105(be)001:1416: skye rga na 'chi'i chu chen 'khrug par bying //
NK105(be)001:1417: sdug bsngal sna tshogs du mas mnyam re thag /
NK105(be)001:1418: de las thar 'dod zhi ba'i sems med la //
NK105(be)001:1419: yang dag lam ston dge ba'i bshes med pas //
NK105(be)001:1420: mtha' med 'khor bar 'khyams pa snying re rje //
NK105(be)001:1421: 'di dag mthong nas yal bar 'dor phod dam //
NK105(be)001:1422: de bas bdag gi lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK105(be)001:1423: dus gsum dge bas 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal dag /
NK105(be)001:1424: skad cig nyid la bral bar shog cig ces //
NK105(be)001:1425: snying khong rus pa'i gting nas bsam par bya //
NK105(be)001:1426: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal mi bzod rtags su bshad //
NK105(be)001:1427: dmigs med snying rjes de rjes mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:1428: rtags ni stong nyid snying rje zung du 'brel //
NK105(be)001:1429: 'bras bu gnod sems rnam 'tshe bral ba'i sems //
NK105(be)001:1430: las rung gdod nas dag pa nyid du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1431: de ltar snying rjes brlan pa'i 'gro ba la //
NK105(be)001:1432: rang rang bde bas gnas te dga' ba bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1433: de yang dmigs yul bde ldan sems can te //
NK105(be)001:1434: rnam pa e ma 'gro ba 'di dag kun //
NK105(be)001:1435: bdag gis bde la dgod par ma dgos par //
NK105(be)001:1436: rang rang bde ba bdag gis rnyed pa rab //
NK105(be)001:1437: da ni ding nas byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK105(be)001:1438: bde zhing skyid pa 'di dang mi 'bral shog /
NK105(be)001:1439: snyam du gcig nas kun la bsgom par bya //
NK105(be)001:1440: rtags su phrag dog med cing dga' ba skye //
NK105(be)001:1441: de rjes mi dmigs bsam gtan dga' ba nyid //
NK105(be)001:1442: lus ngag sems la zhi bde lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:1443: 'bras bu 'byor pas brtan la dga' ba 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1444: de ltar goms rjes byams nas rim par bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1445: de yis bzhi po'i zhen pa rim gyis 'gog /
NK105(be)001:1446: byams bsgoms gnyen bzhin kun la chags pa na //
NK105(be)001:1447: snying rjes sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras zhen pa 'gog /
NK105(be)001:1448: snying rje dman pas dmigs dang bcas pa na //
NK105(be)001:1449: dmigs med dga' bas skyo ba rnam par 'gog /
NK105(be)001:1450: dga' bas sems g.yengs spros la 'chel ba na //
NK105(be)001:1451: nye ring chags bral btang snyoms chen po bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1452: btang snyoms bar ma lung ma bstan bzhin na //
NK105(be)001:1453: sngar bzhin byams sogs rim pas bsgom par bya //
NK105(be)001:1454: de yis 'byongs par sla zhing brtan pa 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1455: goms pa shin tu brtan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK105(be)001:1456: rim dang rim min spel ma thod rgal bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1457: de yis rtogs pa so mar bogs 'byin zhing //
NK105(be)001:1458: shin tu brtan pas ches brtan nyid du 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1459: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu bzhi dag las //
NK105(be)001:1460: rnam smin mngo mtho nges legs gnyis 'thob la //
NK105(be)001:1461: 'dod par lha mi'i lus 'grub phan bde byed //
NK105(be)001:1462: rgyu mthun byed pas de nyid byed pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1463: myong bas mi mthun phyogs bral bde ba 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1464: dbang gis yid 'ong bde zhing rab dag'i yul //
NK105(be)001:1465: 'gro ba mthun cing 'byor pas brgyan par skye //
NK105(be)001:1466: byed pas bzhi po ches cher rab 'phel bas //
NK105(be)001:1467: rang gzhan don gnyis 'byor pa lhun grub 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1468: byams pas zhe sdang med cing longs spyod rdzogs //
NK105(be)001:1469: me long ye shes rab tu thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1470: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni mtshan dpes brgyan //
NK105(be)001:1471: snying rjes 'dod chags med cing chos kyi sku //
NK105(be)001:1472: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes mngon du byed //
NK105(be)001:1473: chos kyi sku ni stobs sogs ma 'dres chos //
NK105(be)001:1474: dga' bas phrag dog med cing sprul pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:1475: bya grub ye shes dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1476: sprul pa'i sku ni ma nges sna tshogs gzugs //
NK105(be)001:1477: lhun gyis grub pa'i sku ste phrin las yin //
NK105(be)001:1478: btang snyoms nga rgyal rmongs med ngo bo nyid //
NK105(be)001:1479: mnyam nyid chos dbyings ye shes mngon du byed //
NK105(be)001:1480: ngo bo nyid sku chos nyid spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:1481: de ltar byams sogs yon tan mtha' yas shing //
NK105(be)001:1482: mtshungs bral lha mi'i ston pas rab basngagasa mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1483: de dag mi ldan lam de phyin ci log /
NK105(be)001:1484: ston pa gzhan la skyabs song lam ngan yin //
NK105(be)001:1485: des gzung lam ni thar pa dri ma med //
NK105(be)001:1486: dus gsum rgyal ba snga phyi'i gshegs shul yin //
NK105(be)001:1487: rgyu yi theg pas sa bon myu gu bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1488: thabs shes sku gnyis bskyed par 'dod na yang //
NK105(be)001:1489: 'bras bu'i theg pas sku yi sgrib pa gnyis //
NK105(be)001:1490: sel byed rkyen gyi rnam par khas len pas //
NK105(be)001:1491: thabs nyid snying rje tshad med lam la brten //
NK105(be)001:1492: don la gcig ste stong nyid snying rje can //
NK105(be)001:1493: rgyu 'bras gnyis kas mthun par nyams su len //
NK105(be)001:1494: gzhan yang thog med dge ba sa bon tshul //
NK105(be)001:1495: ma byas ye nas gnas par mdo nas gsungs //
NK105(be)001:1496: de dang sku gsum ye ldan glo bur gyi //
NK105(be)001:1497: sgrib pas bsgribs te sel 'dod sngags nyid mtshungs //
NK105(be)001:1498: mdor na mdo rgyud lam rnams gcig nyid du //
NK105(be)001:1499: mkhas grub rnams kyis phyi nang bshad pa mdzad //
NK105(be)001:1500: de phyir rgyal sras dam pa'i rjes 'gro zhing //
NK105(be)001:1501: tshad med rnam pa bzhi la 'bad par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1502: de ltar legs gsungs zhi ba'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK105(be)001:1503: 'gro kun sems kyi rnyog pa rab zhi nas //
NK105(be)001:1504: lam gol log dang dman par zhugs pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1505: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:1506: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:1507: tshad med bzhi'i le'u ste bdun pa'o////de ltar tshad med legs par goms pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1508: chos kun rtsa ba byang chub sems gnyis bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1509: de yang nyon mongs srid mtsho mthar 'byin zhing //
NK105(be)001:1510: 'jigs dang mya ngan sdig kun sel byed de //
NK105(be)001:1511: las dang sdug bsngal 'du byed rnam par 'joms //
NK105(be)001:1512: srid nas zhi bar 'gro ba 'dren byed yin //
NK105(be)001:1513: gang la sems pa mngon gyur med na yang //
NK105(be)001:1514: snying rje'i dge rgyun gong nas gong 'phel zhing //
NK105(be)001:1515: mnyam gzhag na yang thabs shes zung du 'brel //
NK105(be)001:1516: lus ngag rtsom pa thams cad don yod cing //
NK105(be)001:1517: lhar bcas 'jig rten kun gyi mchod sdong 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1518: dge gzhan 'bras bu dman te zad pa ltar //
NK105(be)001:1519: rin chen sems zin dge ba mi zad 'phel //
NK105(be)001:1520: ji ltar rgya mtsho dngas pa'i chu 'bab dang //
NK105(be)001:1521: sa gzhi bzang por lo thog phun tshogs bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1522: kun gyi rtsa ba sa bon snying rje'i bdag /
NK105(be)001:1523: srid pa na yang bde ba'i 'bras mang zhing //
NK105(be)001:1524: zhi ba'i rang bzhin byang chub mchog gi rgyu //
NK105(be)001:1525: rin chen sems legs bskyed la 'bad par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1526: de ni dpal rgyas yid bzhin bum pa bzang //
NK105(be)001:1527: 'gro ba'i nad gso bde 'byung sman gyi mchog /
NK105(be)001:1528: ye shes nyi ma gdung sel zla ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1529: mkha' bzhin dri med yon tan rgyu skar tshogs //
NK105(be)001:1530: rtag tu phan bde byed pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK105(be)001:1531: bsam yas bsod nams sprin tshogs dpag tu med //
NK105(be)001:1532: rgyal ba'i yon tan shin tu rmad byung dang //
NK105(be)001:1533: chos kyi dbyings ltar dpag yas rgya che'o //
NK105(be)001:1534: sems bskyed pa ni tshad med 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1535: yang dag sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1536: smon dang 'jug pa'i rang bzhin gnyis yin no //
NK105(be)001:1537: de yang bsam pas smon dang sbyor bas khyab //
NK105(be)001:1538: 'gro bar 'dod dang 'gro ba nyid bzhin no //
NK105(be)001:1539: smon pa tshad med bzhi yi ngo bo la //
NK105(be)001:1540: 'jug pa pha rol phyin pa drug tu 'dod //
NK105(be)001:1541: gang gis phyogs mtha' gtugs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK105(be)001:1542: bskal pa bye ba mang por bsnyen bkur te //
NK105(be)001:1543: rang nyid legs pa tsam zhig don gnyer ba'i //
NK105(be)001:1544: bsod nams de yis smon pa'i char mi phod //
NK105(be)001:1545: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal nyung zad sel ba'i blo //
NK105(be)001:1546: skad cig skyes pas ngan song thar gyur zhing //
NK105(be)001:1547: lha mi'i bde ba dpag med myong bar gsungs //
NK105(be)001:1548: de bas 'jug pa'i phan yon mtha' yas te //
NK105(be)001:1549: dngos su sbyor bas yang dag khyab pa'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1550: skad cig sbyor bas khyab pa'i sems mchog gis //
NK105(be)001:1551: bskal pa mang po'i tshogs gnyis bzlums par bshad //
NK105(be)001:1552: de phyir grangs med gsum sogs gsungs pa kun //
NK105(be)001:1553: myur du rdzogs dang ring du rdzogs pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1554: tshe gcig grol ba blo yi stobs la reg /
NK105(be)001:1555: de yang thabs dang brtson 'grus shes rab mchog /
NK105(be)001:1556: gsum gyis bsgrub gang bla med stobs che'o //
NK105(be)001:1557: 'di ni snying rje'i ljon shing snying po can //
NK105(be)001:1558: 'gro ba'i khur chen legs par khyer ba ni //
NK105(be)001:1559: tshangs sogs 'jig rten na yang sngon med cing //
NK105(be)001:1560: rang nyid phyir yang rmi lam ma rmis na //
NK105(be)001:1561: gzhan phyir smos ci 'tshal ba'i byang chub sems //
NK105(be)001:1562: snga na med pa 'khrungs la dga' ba bskyed //
NK105(be)001:1563: de yang dge ba'i bshes las 'byung ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1564: yid bzhin dag las 'dod dgu'i char 'bebs bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1565: skyon bral yon tan rdzogs pa'i bla ma yis //
NK105(be)001:1566: skal bzang slob ma spro ba bskyed pa ni //
NK105(be)001:1567: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs thar pa'i phan yon sogs //
NK105(be)001:1568: thog ma bar dang mthar dge'i chos rnams dang //
NK105(be)001:1569: byang chub sems kyi basngagasa pa mtha' yas brjod //
NK105(be)001:1570: gnas gtsang mchod pas mdzes shing nyams dga' bar //
NK105(be)001:1571: rgyal ba'i sku gzugs la sogs sta gon bya //
NK105(be)001:1572: nam mkha'i gnas su nam mkha' gang ba yi //
NK105(be)001:1573: rgyal ba sras bcas rgya mtsho'i sprin phung bsam //
NK105(be)001:1574: 'di ni rang gi sems stobs dri med dang //
NK105(be)001:1575: mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug rnams kyi thugs rje yis //
NK105(be)001:1576: ji ltar bsams pa de bzhin 'grub par gsungs //
NK105(be)001:1577: de nas thal sbyar me tog snyim bkang nas //
NK105(be)001:1578: spyan drang bzhugs gsol khrus rgyan gos sogs dbul //
NK105(be)001:1579: yid 'ong rdzing bu'i nang na gnas pa yi //
NK105(be)001:1581: lag gnyis spyi bor thal sbyar bstod dbyangs bcas //
NK105(be)001:1582: lus dpag med par sprul nas gus phyag 'tshal //
NK105(be)001:1583: sa 'di rir bcas rgya mtsho'i rdul snyed du //
NK105(be)001:1584: bsod nams de 'dra 'jig rten gsum na med //
NK105(be)001:1585: lus btud dbang chen bar gyi rdul rnams dang //
NK105(be)001:1586: mnyam pa'i grangs snyed 'khor los sgyur 'gro zhing //
NK105(be)001:1587: mthar thug zhi ba mchog gi go 'phang 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1588: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK105(be)001:1589: mchod pa bla med rgya chen rnams kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1590: me tog spos dang mar me zhal zas chu //
NK105(be)001:1591: bla re 'phan lding gdugs dang rol mo'i sgra //
NK105(be)001:1592: rgyal mtshan rnga yab rdza rnga la sogs dang //
NK105(be)001:1593: lus dang longs spyod mkho dgu'i yo byad kyis //
NK105(be)001:1594: 'gro ba'i bla ma dkon mchog sras bcas mchod //
NK105(be)001:1595: lha sogs 'jig rten kun na yid 'ong ba'i //
NK105(be)001:1596: gzhal med khang brtsegs rin chen d+r+wa ba can //
NK105(be)001:1597: glu gar sil snyan bstod dbyangs char 'bab cing //
NK105(be)001:1598: rgyan mchog brgya phrag mnga' ba rnams kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1599: rin chen ri bo nags tshal pad+ma'i mtsho //
NK105(be)001:1600: ngang mo'i 'gros kyis gnyer ba de dag dang //
NK105(be)001:1601: sman sogs dri zhim ngad ldang dpag bsam shing //
NK105(be)001:1602: me tog 'bras bu dud pa'i tshogs kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1603: 'dab stong g.yo bas bung ba bzung ba yi //
NK105(be)001:1604: lag pa'i gdu bu ku mu tas mtshan zhing //
NK105(be)001:1605: sprin bral nyi zla'i zer gyis rab phye ba'i //
NK105(be)001:1606: ut+pa la sogs yid 'ong rnams kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1607: tsan+dana bsil ba'i kha yi sbubs bskyod pa'i //
NK105(be)001:1608: dri zhim ser bu bde ba'i ngad rnams dang //
NK105(be)001:1609: phug dang brag ri sman ljongs nyams dga' ba //
NK105(be)001:1610: chu bsil rdzing bu gang ba rnams kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1611: ston ka'i mtshan mo dkar ba'i ri bong 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:1612: gza' bral rgyu skar phreng bas bskor ba dang //
NK105(be)001:1613: nyin byed 'od stong dra bas mdzes 'bar ba //
NK105(be)001:1614: gling bzhi'i 'jig rten rgyan gyur rnams kyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1615: khor yug rir bcas bye ba phrag brgya'i zhing //
NK105(be)001:1616: ma lus yongs bkod 'dod dgus 'byor pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1617: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rgya mtsho'i rdul snyed kun //
NK105(be)001:1618: blo yis blangs te thub dbang sras bcas mchod //
NK105(be)001:1619: bum bzang dpag bsam shing dang 'dod 'jo'i ba //
NK105(be)001:1620: rgyal srid bdun dang bkra shis rdzas brgyad dang //
NK105(be)001:1621: nye ba'i rin chen bdun sogs rgya che bas //
NK105(be)001:1622: yon gnas dam pa thugs rje che rnams mchod //
NK105(be)001:1623: ting 'dzin yid kyis nam mkha'i dbyings khyab par //
NK105(be)001:1624: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod sprin rgya mtshos mchod //
NK105(be)001:1625: me tog sprin mdzes lding khang mdzes 'bar ba //
NK105(be)001:1626: spos dang sman sbyar bdud rtsi'i sprin phung dang //
NK105(be)001:1627: gzi ldan sgron ma zhal zas rol mo'i sprin //
NK105(be)001:1628: bstod dbyangs yan lag rgya mtsho'i sprin gyis mchod //
NK105(be)001:1629: 'jug pa'i sprin can shin tu mtha' yas pa //
NK105(be)001:1630: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar sogs //
NK105(be)001:1631: mchod pa'i lha mo sna tshogs sprin 'phro bas //
NK105(be)001:1632: rgyal ba sras bcas ma lus mnyes gyur cig /
NK105(be)001:1633: thog med dus nas goms pa'i bag chags kyis //
NK105(be)001:1634: las dang nyon mongs sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NK105(be)001:1635: srid pa'i rgyur gyur de kun bshags par bgyi //
NK105(be)001:1636: 'gro ba'i bsod nams phung po mtha' yas la //
NK105(be)001:1637: rtag par bdag ni rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK105(be)001:1638: ma lus skye dgu'i tshogs rnams bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1639: chos kyi 'khor lo bla med bskor bar bskul //
NK105(be)001:1640: ding nas srid pa'i rgya mtsho ma stongs par //
NK105(be)001:1641: mya ngan mi 'da' rtag tu bzhugs par gsol //
NK105(be)001:1642: dge ba de yis bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK105(be)001:1643: ma lus phyam gcig sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK105(be)001:1644: ji ltar khrus kyis sbyangs pa'i ras yug dag /
NK105(be)001:1645: tshon gyis bsgyur bas kha dog gsal ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1646: de ltar sngon du 'gro bas sems sbyangs pa'i //
NK105(be)001:1647: rgyud las dngos gzhi'i sems mchog gsal bar skye //
NK105(be)001:1648: 'di ni bsod nams 'bras bu tshad med de //
NK105(be)001:1649: chos dbyings ji bzhin nam mkha'i dbyings kun khyab //
NK105(be)001:1650: de nas sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs mchog la //
NK105(be)001:1651: lan gsum bar du skyabs su 'gro byas te //
NK105(be)001:1652: mgon po sras dang bcas rnams dgongs su gsol //
NK105(be)001:1653: ji ltar sngon gyi bde gshegs sras bcas kyis //
NK105(be)001:1654: byang chub thugs bskyed bslab la gnas pa ltar //
NK105(be)001:1655: ding nas bdag gis 'gro la phan don du //
NK105(be)001:1656: byang chub sems bskyed bslab la gnas par bgyi //
NK105(be)001:1657: ma brgal ba rnams bdag gis bsgral bar bgyi //
NK105(be)001:1658: ma grol ba rnams bdag gis dgrol bgyi zhing //
NK105(be)001:1659: dbugs ma phyung rnams bdag gis dbugs dbyung ste //
NK105(be)001:1660: sems can rnams ni mya ngan 'das la 'god //
NK105(be)001:1661: de ltar nyin dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK105(be)001:1662: byang chub sems gnyis bskyed la 'bad par bya //
NK105(be)001:1663: brjod pa dang pos smon pa sems bskyed la //
NK105(be)001:1664: gnyis pas 'jug pa sems bskyed gsum pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1665: gnyis ka brtan zhing dag pa thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1666: ding nas bdag ni 'gro kun nyer 'tsho'i gzhi //
NK105(be)001:1667: rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i ming yang thob //
NK105(be)001:1668: srid na mi 'jigs 'gro ba'i don byed cing //
NK105(be)001:1669: rtag tu phan pa 'ba' zhig lhur len pas //
NK105(be)001:1670: mi yi srid pa don dang bcas par gyur //
NK105(be)001:1671: da ni sems gtsang dge ba'i sa gzhi la //
NK105(be)001:1672: byang chub sems gnyis myu gu rab bskyed de //
NK105(be)001:1673: de gzung dag pa spel phyir brtson par bya //
NK105(be)001:1674: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal bdag gis blang bya zhing //
NK105(be)001:1675: bdag gi bde bas 'gro ba bder gyur te //
NK105(be)001:1676: byang chub bar du de dang mi 'bral shog /
NK105(be)001:1677: snyam du gtong len spel mar sbyang bya zhing //
NK105(be)001:1678: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi po bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1679: de yi mi mthun phyogs spang sems bsrung bya //
NK105(be)001:1680: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug spyad //
NK105(be)001:1681: de yi mi mthun phyogs spang brtson par bya //
NK105(be)001:1682: rtag tu dran dang shes bzhin bag yod kyis //
NK105(be)001:1683: mi dge spang zhing dge chos rgya mtsho bsgrub //
NK105(be)001:1684: byang chub sems gnyis mi nyams bslab bya ste //
NK105(be)001:1685: log par lta sogs rgyal po'i ltung ba lnga //
NK105(be)001:1686: grong sogs blon po'i lnga dang phal pa'i brgyad //
NK105(be)001:1687: thun mong gnyis te nyi shu ltung byed la //
NK105(be)001:1688: de dang phyogs mthun nyes byas shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:1689: de dag mi ldan ltung dang nyes med de //
NK105(be)001:1690: dge ba'i phyogs mthun bslab byar shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:1691: mdor na nag po'i chos bzhi spang bya zhing //
NK105(be)001:1692: dkar po'i chos bzhi dag la nan tan bya //
NK105(be)001:1693: mchod 'os slu dang 'gyod pa med la bskyed //
NK105(be)001:1694: dam pa rnams la mi snyan sgrogs pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1695: 'gro ba'i nang na g.yo dang sgyus spyod pa //
NK105(be)001:1696: nag po'i chos bzhi lags pas spang 'tshal lo //
NK105(be)001:1697: dam pa bsten zhing yon tan basngagasa pa brjod //
NK105(be)001:1698: sems can rnams ni yang dag dge la bskul //
NK105(be)001:1699: rgyal sras rnams la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed //
NK105(be)001:1700: lhag pa'i bsam pas 'gro la phan bde byed //
NK105(be)001:1701: dkar po'i chos rab bzhi po bsten par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1702: rang don las kyang gzhan phan gtsor 'dzin pa //
NK105(be)001:1703: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bslab pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1704: gzhan don 'gyur na lus ngag mi dge bdun //
NK105(be)001:1705: gnang ba'i skabs yod don la dge ba yin //
NK105(be)001:1706: yid gsum nam yang gnang ba'i skabs med do //
NK105(be)001:1707: rang don zhi bde 'dod pa'i dge ba yang //
NK105(be)001:1708: rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i ltung ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1709: gzhan phyir phan na mi dge gang lags pa //
NK105(be)001:1710: de yang bslab bya lags par rgyal bas gsungs //
NK105(be)001:1711: rgyal sras de yang rnam pa gsum nyid de //
NK105(be)001:1712: rang nyid grol nas 'gro ba sgrol 'dod pa //
NK105(be)001:1713: rgyal po lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK105(be)001:1714: rang dang 'gro ba mnyam du thar 'dod pa //
NK105(be)001:1715: gru pa lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK105(be)001:1716: 'gro ba bsgral nas rang nyid zhi 'dod pa //
NK105(be)001:1717: rdzi bo lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa' gsum //
NK105(be)001:1718: rim bzhin grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum dang //
NK105(be)001:1719: bdun dang gsum gyis grol ba thob pa ni //
NK105(be)001:1720: dbang po'i rim pa lags par mdo las gsungs //
NK105(be)001:1721: rgyal sras rnams kyis kun la bslab pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1722: gtso bor pha rol phyin pa drug la bslab //
NK105(be)001:1723: 'gro ba dbul bas nyam thag mthong nas ni //
NK105(be)001:1724: zas gos rta dang shing rta glang po sogs //
NK105(be)001:1725: mkho dgu'i yo byad dpag med gtong ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1726: bu dang bu mo la sogs gtong ba che //
NK105(be)001:1727: mgo dang mig sogs shin tu gtong ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1728: zang zing dang ni chos kyis phan pa bsgrub //
NK105(be)001:1729: des ni rang gi ser sna'i tshogs 'joms shing //
NK105(be)001:1730: gzhan gyi 'byor pa nye bar skye bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1731: lhag pa'i tshul khrims kyis ni rgyud bsdams shing //
NK105(be)001:1732: sems kyis dge ba zhi ba rnams bsgrubs la //
NK105(be)001:1733: shes rab kyis ni don gnyis phun tshogs 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1734: sdom dang chos sdud sems can don byed de //
NK105(be)001:1735: rgyal sras rnams kyis tshul khrims gsum rtag bsrung //
NK105(be)001:1736: khyim pas dge bsnyen bsnyen gnas smon 'jug la //
NK105(be)001:1737: rab tu byung bas dge slong dge tshul dang //
NK105(be)001:1738: dge slob ma yi sdom pa gang yin steng //
NK105(be)001:1739: byang chub sems gnyis bsrung ba tshul khrims yin //
NK105(be)001:1740: phyi nang gnod pa sna tshogs sdug bsngal la //
NK105(be)001:1741: ji mi snyam dang snying rjes chos la som //
NK105(be)001:1742: dmigs med bzod pa gsum yang bsgrub par bya //
NK105(be)001:1743: zhe sdang lta bu'i sdig pa 'ga' med la //
NK105(be)001:1744: bzod mtshungs dka' thub bsod nams gzhan med pas //
NK105(be)001:1745: sna tshogs tshul gyis bzod la nan tan du //
NK105(be)001:1746: khro ba'i me chen 'jil la brtson par bya //
NK105(be)001:1747: gnod pa'i yul rnams mi bsrun grangs med pas //
NK105(be)001:1748: re re zhing yang gdul bar yod mi lang //
NK105(be)001:1749: sems gcig btul bas thams cad dul 'gyur ba //
NK105(be)001:1750: sems 'dul brtul zhugs bsrung la nan tan mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1751: gnod la brten nas bzod pa'i legs pa 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1752: snying rje dang ni byams sogs yon tan skye //
NK105(be)001:1753: byang chub grogs gyur dgra la ston pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1754: gus dang spro bas bzod pa nye bar bsten //
NK105(be)001:1755: gzhan yang bdag nyid med na mi 'byung la //
NK105(be)001:1756: brag ca bzhin du phan tshun brten pa can //
NK105(be)001:1757: rang gis nyes gyur gnod pa'i tshogs rab 'di //
NK105(be)001:1758: 'phral gyi rkyen dang sngon las rgyus bskyed phyir //
NK105(be)001:1759: 'di 'byung rigs te las zad thabs 'di la //
NK105(be)001:1760: ci nas sems 'dul gcig pur bsran tshugs bya //
NK105(be)001:1761: mi 'dod thog tu bab la mi dga' btang //
NK105(be)001:1762: bcos su yod na mi dgar ci dgos la //
NK105(be)001:1763: med na phan pa med pas ci byar yod //
NK105(be)001:1764: de bas rkyen rnams bzod la nan tan bya //
NK105(be)001:1765: brtags na mkha' bzhin stong pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK105(be)001:1766: dga' dang mi dga' shor god legs nyes med //
NK105(be)001:1767: de la gnyis su bzung yang don med kyis //
NK105(be)001:1768: thams cad mnyam nyid ngang la nan tan mdzod //
NK105(be)001:1769: gang la brtson pa'i rang bzhin dge la spro //
NK105(be)001:1770: de la dge chos mi zad sprin bzhin 'du //
NK105(be)001:1771: dri zhim pad+ma'i tshal du bung ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1772: de yi mi mthun phyogs gang le lo gsum //
NK105(be)001:1773: bya ba ngan zhen sgyid lug bdag nyid brnyas //
NK105(be)001:1774: legs pa mi 'grub nyes kun 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK105(be)001:1775: phun tshogs nyams la rgud pa skye bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1776: brtson 'grus ldan pa 'jig rten gyis bstod cing //
NK105(be)001:1777: brtson 'grus ldan pa mi yi bsam pa 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1778: brtson 'grus ldan pa yon tan tshogs 'phel zhing //
NK105(be)001:1779: brtson 'grus ldan pa mya ngan 'da' bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1780: de yang 'jig rten dge chos mchog rnams dang //
NK105(be)001:1781: 'jig rten 'das pa'i lam ni gang yin pa //
NK105(be)001:1782: zag bcas zag pa med pa'i chos rnams la //
NK105(be)001:1783: mi dge spang zhing dge ba bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1784: 'bad rtsol brtson pas yang dag gnas par bya //
NK105(be)001:1785: ji srid sangs rgyas ma thob bar du ni //
NK105(be)001:1786: ches cher gong du yang dag 'gror yod pas //
NK105(be)001:1787: de srid mi ngal 'bad pas brtson 'grus brtsam //
NK105(be)001:1788: bsam gtan 'dod pas rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi spang //
NK105(be)001:1789: yul gyi dga' ba ston ka'i sprin 'dra zhing //
NK105(be)001:1790: glog ltar mi brtan g.yo ba'i rang bzhin te //
NK105(be)001:1791: longs spyod mi rtag sgyu ma'i khang bzangs 'dra //
NK105(be)001:1792: nam yang yid brtan mi rung de spangs te //
NK105(be)001:1793: myur ba nyid du zhi ba'i nags 'dab bsten //
NK105(be)001:1794: 'dod pa rnams ni phung krol bskyed pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1795: bsag dang bsrung dang tshol bas sdug bsngal zhing //
NK105(be)001:1796: khengs dang sred dang 'jungs pas ser sna 'phel //
NK105(be)001:1798: 'dod pa chung dang chog shes ldan par bya //
NK105(be)001:1799: lus rma ji snyed sdug bsngal khyab pa ltar //
NK105(be)001:1800: nor mang ji snyed sdug bsngal de bas mang //
NK105(be)001:1801: yo byad bsnyungs rnams bde ba mtha' yas te //
NK105(be)001:1802: 'tshe ba nyung zhing dgra rkun 'jigs pa med //
NK105(be)001:1803: kun gyis bstod cing 'phags pa'i lam la gnas //
NK105(be)001:1804: bya ba nyung zhing sems las chung bas na //
NK105(be)001:1805: rtag tu 'dod pa chung la bslab par bya //
NK105(be)001:1806: byis dang 'grogs pa'i nyes pa tshad med de //
NK105(be)001:1807: sdig pa 'phel zhing mi dge ngang gis 'go //
NK105(be)001:1808: dge ba 'grib cing rtsod dang nyon mongs skye //
NK105(be)001:1809: byas pa mi gzo nam yang mgu bar dka' //
NK105(be)001:1810: don med bya ba mang zhing 'du 'dzis g.yeng //
NK105(be)001:1811: me dang sbrul dang gcan gzan khrod 'dra ba'i //
NK105(be)001:1812: byis pa rnams las thag ring 'byol bar bya //
NK105(be)001:1813: ji srid sems la brtan pa ma thob par //
NK105(be)001:1814: phyi rol yul gyis rab tu slu bas na //
NK105(be)001:1815: dben pa'i nags su spro bas gnas par bya //
NK105(be)001:1816: ji srid skyes bu bzhi yis bteg pa'i lus //
NK105(be)001:1817: ngud mo'i sgra dang bcas par ma gyur bar //
NK105(be)001:1818: bdag ni zhi ba'i dgon par rab phyogs te //
NK105(be)001:1819: lus sems 'du 'dzi'i dgra las rgyal bar bya //
NK105(be)001:1820: nags ni chu gtsang me tog 'bras mang zhing //
NK105(be)001:1821: brag ri'i phug dang rdo leb khang bzangs mang //
NK105(be)001:1822: dud pa'i ljon shing grib mas brgyan pa'i khrod //
NK105(be)001:1823: bya dang ri dgas mang po gar byed cing //
NK105(be)001:1824: chu 'gram me tog bung ba glu len mdzes //
NK105(be)001:1825: spos dang sman sogs dri zhim ngad ldang zhing //
NK105(be)001:1826: dben zhing nyams dga' bsam gtan ngang gis 'phel //
NK105(be)001:1827: dus bzhir dga' bas pad+ma'i mtsho 'dra zhing //
NK105(be)001:1828: so ga dbyar dang ston dus dgun dang dpyid //
NK105(be)001:1829: rim gyis 'gyur bas mi rtag skyo shas 'phel //
NK105(be)001:1830: dur khrod rus pa 'thor ba'i tshul mthong nas //
NK105(be)001:1831: bdag gi lus kyang de 'dra'i ngang tshul can //
NK105(be)001:1832: so sor 'gyes chos can du mthong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1833: 'dus byas snying po med pa'i 'khor ba la //
NK105(be)001:1834: dga' ba'i blo gros gang yin ring du byed //
NK105(be)001:1835: rtsod dang nyon mongs med cing rtag zhi bas //
NK105(be)001:1836: rang gi sems ni las rung bde ba 'thob //
NK105(be)001:1837: de 'dra'i nags ni rgyal ba rnams kyis basngagasa //
NK105(be)001:1838: srid la skyo bas dgon par rab phyogs te //
NK105(be)001:1839: gom pa bdun tsam bor ba'i bsod nams ni //
NK105(be)001:1840: gang gis bskal pa gang+g+aa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK105(be)001:1841: bskal par mchod pa'i bsod nams phung po yis //
NK105(be)001:1842: snga ma'i bsod nams brgya stong char mi phod //
NK105(be)001:1843: de phyir zhi ba'i nags 'dab bsten par bya //
NK105(be)001:1844: der ni stan la skyil krung rab bcas nas //
NK105(be)001:1845: rtse gcig sems la mi g.yo mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:1846: byis pa nyes spyod don rab 'byed pa dang //
NK105(be)001:1847: de bzhin gshegs dge'i bsam gtan dam pa bsgrub //
NK105(be)001:1848: bsam gtan bzhi dang de bzhin gzugs med bzhi //
NK105(be)001:1849: lam ma zhugs dang zhugs zin 'phags rnams kyis //
NK105(be)001:1850: ting 'dzin gsum gyi ming rnams shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:1851: des ni 'dod yon dga' ba'i sems spong zhing //
NK105(be)001:1852: rig dang mngon shes ting 'dzin mngon par 'grub //
NK105(be)001:1853: spyan dang rdzu 'phrul sems la rang dbang bsgyur //
NK105(be)001:1854: shes rab gsum ste thos bsam sgom pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:1855: lhag mthong grub pas nyon mongs tshogs spong zhing //
NK105(be)001:1856: chos dang chos can gnas lugs rab shes nas //
NK105(be)001:1857: srid pa'i grong las mya ngan 'das zhir 'gro //
NK105(be)001:1858: snang 'di gdod nas ma skyes gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1859: ngo bo med la sna tshogs snang ba ste //
NK105(be)001:1860: rang bzhin dag pa'i rten 'brel mthong nas ni //
NK105(be)001:1861: mi gnas mchog gi go 'phang myur du reg /
NK105(be)001:1862: shes rab ldan pa thabs kyis grol 'gyur te //
NK105(be)001:1863: ji ltar dug la sngags kyis btab pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1864: shes rab med na thabs kyis 'ching 'gyur te //
NK105(be)001:1865: sman nyid nad du song bas gdung ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1866: de phyir gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shes rab bskyed //
NK105(be)001:1867: pha rol phyin pa drug la spyod pa na //
NK105(be)001:1868: sgyu ma'i skye bo ji bzhin shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:1869: 'khor gsum mi rtog dge ba'i tshogs gnyis kyis //
NK105(be)001:1870: rgyal ba'i go 'phang zhi ba thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:1871: de ltar dge legs sprin gyi bzhon pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1872: 'gro sems gtsang ma'i lo thog legs bskrun te //
NK105(be)001:1873: srid pa'i nyes tshogs dbul bas rab phongs pa'i //
NK105(be)001:1874: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:1875: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:1876: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o////de ltar byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK105(be)001:1877: gsang sngags phyi nang bskyed rdzogs don la 'jug /
NK105(be)001:1878: de yang thabs mang dka' ba med phyir dang //
NK105(be)001:1879: don gcig na yang 'jug tshul ma rmongs dang //
NK105(be)001:1880: dbang po shin tu rnon po'i dbang mdzad de //
NK105(be)001:1881: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla na med bzhi bstan //
NK105(be)001:1882: dus dang mi rigs dbang po'i rim pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1883: rdzogs ldan sum ldan nyis ldan rtsod ldan dang //
NK105(be)001:1884: bram ze rje'u rigs rgyal rigs gdol pa'am dmangs //
NK105(be)001:1885: rtul po 'bring rnon shin tu rnon po la //
NK105(be)001:1886: khrus dang gtsang sbra gtsor ston bya ba'i rgyud //
NK105(be)001:1887: lus ngag bya dang sems kyi sgom pa kun //
NK105(be)001:1888: cha mnyam ston pa spyod pa'i rgyud sde dang //
NK105(be)001:1889: sgom pa gtsor ston lus ngag spyod pa kun //
NK105(be)001:1890: grogs tsam ston pa rnal 'byor rgyud dang ni //
NK105(be)001:1891: sgo gsum bya bral gzung 'dzin mi dmigs par //
NK105(be)001:1892: sems kyi chos nyid 'od gsal brtul zhugs mchog /
NK105(be)001:1893: gtsang sbra chung rnams ngor ni rnal 'byor che //
NK105(be)001:1894: de yang bya spyod rnal 'byor thub pa rgyud //
NK105(be)001:1895: k+r+ai ya u pa yo ga zhes bya'o //
NK105(be)001:1896: de dag gsang sngags phyi ste lha rnams kyang //
NK105(be)001:1897: yab yum zung 'brel bsgom par mi nus shing //
NK105(be)001:1898: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga sogs bsten mi byed //
NK105(be)001:1899: gtsang sbra kun du spyod pas gnas pa yin //
NK105(be)001:1900: rnal 'byor bla med rgyud la'ang gsum yin te //
NK105(be)001:1901: pha ma gnyis su med pa bla na med //
NK105(be)001:1902: bskyed rdzogs gnyis med gtso bor ston pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1903: ma h+aa a nu a ti zhes bya'o //
NK105(be)001:1904: lha yang 'khril sbyor dam rdzas khyad par can //
NK105(be)001:1905: gtsang btsog gnyis med thams cad ro gcig tu //
NK105(be)001:1906: dkyil 'khor gcig gi rol par ston pa yin //
NK105(be)001:1907: bya bas rang nyid dman la lha nyid mchog /
NK105(be)001:1908: rje khol tshul du bsgrub pas dngos grub len //
NK105(be)001:1909: spyod pas rang dang lha nyid mnyam par blta //
NK105(be)001:1910: rang nyid dam tshig mdun du ye shes lha //
NK105(be)001:1911: grogs po'i tshul gyis dngos grub len pa yin //
NK105(be)001:1912: rnal 'byor dngos gzhir gnyis su med pa la //
NK105(be)001:1913: sbyor rjes lha ni dgug gshegs gnyis su byed //
NK105(be)001:1914: chu la chu bzhag gnyis med dngos grub len //
NK105(be)001:1915: ma h+aas rlung dang bskyed rim thabs gtso la //
NK105(be)001:1916: a nus khams dang rdzogs rim shes rab gtso //
NK105(be)001:1917: a tis thams cad gnyis med ye shes gtso //
NK105(be)001:1918: kun kyang chos kun ye nas mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:1919: yin par shes pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len //
NK105(be)001:1920: bdag dang 'gro kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK105(be)001:1921: phung po khams dang skye mched la sogs kun //
NK105(be)001:1922: dkyil 'khor gcig tu gsal btab rim gnyis bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1923: de yang skye bzhi'i rim pas sgom tshul bzhi //
NK105(be)001:1924: sgong skyes bag chags sbyang phyir sngon 'gro'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:1925: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bskyed rim mdor bsdus nas //
NK105(be)001:1926: bsod nams zhing rab spyan drangs mchod pa'i mthar //
NK105(be)001:1927: rang bzhin med bsgom tshogs gnyis sngon song nas //
NK105(be)001:1928: gdod kyis bskyed rdzogs rgyas par bsgom pa ni //
NK105(be)001:1929: thog mar sgo nga de las bya skye bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1930: mdor bsdus rgyas pa'i bskyed rdzogs rim pas bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1931: mngal skyes bag chags sbyang phyir bstan pa ni //
NK105(be)001:1932: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed stong las sa bon dang //
NK105(be)001:1933: phyag mtshan las ni sku dang 'od zer sogs //
NK105(be)001:1934: rim gyis rgyas par bsgom gyis sngar bzhin du //
NK105(be)001:1935: mdor bsdus sngon du mi 'gro'i bskyed rdzogs ni //
NK105(be)001:1936: ji ltar rlung sems thig le dkar dmar las //
NK105(be)001:1937: mer nur ltar dang mkhrang gyur la sogs nas //
NK105(be)001:1938: lus yongs rdzogs te btsa' ba'i bar bzhin no //
NK105(be)001:1939: drod gsher las skyes bag chags sbyang bya'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1940: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed stong las lha rnams kyi //
NK105(be)001:1941: mtshan tsam brjod las lhar gsal bskyed rdzogs bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1942: ji ltar drod gsher 'dus pas grub pa'i lus //
NK105(be)001:1943: shin tu 'grub par sla bas btsa' ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1944: sa bon phyag mtshan spros pa dgos pa med //
NK105(be)001:1945: bardzusa te skye ba'i bag chags sbyang bya'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:1946: skad cig tsam gyis wal gyis bskyed rdzogs bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1947: ji ltar rdzus skyes skad cig snang ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1948: ming las rim gyis bskyed rdzogs bsgom mi dgos //
NK105(be)001:1949: de ltar sgom tshul rnam pa bzhi nyid kyang //
NK105(be)001:1950: gtso bor skye ba gang bsdus des bsgoms la //
NK105(be)001:1951: bag chags sbyang phyir kun gyis de bzhin bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1952: khyad par las dang po yis sgong skyes bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1953: cung zad brtan pas mngal skyes bzhin bsgoms la //
NK105(be)001:1954: brtan pa che bas drod gsher skyes bzhin bsgom //
NK105(be)001:1955: shin tu goms pa yang dag brtan pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1956: rdzus skyes bzhin du skad cig dkrong bskyed bya //
NK105(be)001:1957: rdzogs rim de yang snang bcas snang med de //
NK105(be)001:1958: bskyed rim bsdus nam mkha' la sprin dengs bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1959: mi dmigs ngang du 'jog pa snang ba med //
NK105(be)001:1960: bskyed rim de nyid rdzogs par shes bya ste //
NK105(be)001:1961: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:1962: ma yengs bsgom pa snang bcas rim pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:1963: las dang po yis bskyed rim zhen pa dgag /
NK105(be)001:1964: snang la bden par zhen pa'i gnyen po byed //
NK105(be)001:1965: brtan pa rnams kyis rdzogs rim zhen pa dgag /
NK105(be)001:1966: stong la mtshan mar zhen pa'i gnyen po byed //
NK105(be)001:1967: phyi nas gang snang bskyed rim thabs nyid la //
NK105(be)001:1968: 'dzin med shes pa rdzogs rim shes rab nyid //
NK105(be)001:1969: dus rnams kun du 'du 'bral med par 'chang //
NK105(be)001:1970: bskyed rim snang 'di'i bden zhen 'gog pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1971: rdzogs rim sgyu mar zhen pa'i rtog pa spong //
NK105(be)001:1972: gang la snang stong bden zhen med pa na //
NK105(be)001:1973: bskyed rdzogs gnyis med rang bzhin dag pa yin //
NK105(be)001:1974: 'di ni mthar thug rdo rje'i theg pa ste //
NK105(be)001:1975: dbang po rnon po tshe 'dir rdzogs sangs rgya //
NK105(be)001:1976: de rjes gdul bya'i 'jig rten gang yod der //
NK105(be)001:1977: sangs rgyas mdzad pa sna tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:1978: 'di ni grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK105(be)001:1979: nye lam sbas pa shin tu zab mo ste //
NK105(be)001:1980: skal bzang tshe 'dir grol 'dod rnams kyis bsten //
NK105(be)001:1981: de yang gang mos rgyud sde'i rim pa la //
NK105(be)001:1982: brten nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub bsgrub par bya //
NK105(be)001:1983: thog mar rig gtad rjes gnang dbang la sogs //
NK105(be)001:1984: rang rang gzhung nas gsungs pa'i lung mnos te //
NK105(be)001:1985: rang gi sems 'di yongs su smin par bya //
NK105(be)001:1986: khyad par mchog gsang rnal 'byor chen po'i lam //
NK105(be)001:1987: smin byed dbang bzhi grol byed bskyed rdzogs te //
NK105(be)001:1988: bum dbang lus dang gsang bas ngag dang ni //
NK105(be)001:1989: shes rab ye shes yid dang tshig dbang gis //
NK105(be)001:1990: bag chags mtha' dag sbyong zhing dngos grub ster //
NK105(be)001:1991: dang po gsum gyis bsod nams tshogs rdzogs la //
NK105(be)001:1992: bzhi pas ye shes tshogs rdzogs de bzhin du //
NK105(be)001:1993: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib kun sbyong //
NK105(be)001:1994: de phyir smin byed dbang bzhi thob pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1995: grol byed bskyed rdzogs don la bslab par bya //
NK105(be)001:1996: 'dir ni dbang rdzogs dam tshig ldan pa yis //
NK105(be)001:1997: gnyis med a ti'i dgongs par 'jug 'dod pas //
NK105(be)001:1998: bde ba'i stan la skyil krung rab bcas nas //
NK105(be)001:1999: skyabs su 'gro dang byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK105(be)001:2000: chos rnams thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa //
NK105(be)001:2001: rang bzhin spros dang bral ba'i ngang nyid las //
NK105(be)001:2002: h'u las steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad du //
NK105(be)001:2003: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo yangs shing rgya che ba //
NK105(be)001:2004: rtsibs bcu khro bo bcu yis mtshan pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2005: phyi nang me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na dpal //
NK105(be)001:2006: kun du bzang po'i dkyil 'khor chen po ni //
NK105(be)001:2007: sgo bzhi gru bzhi rta babs bzhis brgyan zhing //
NK105(be)001:2008: rtsig pa lnga dang 'dod yon snam bu dang //
NK105(be)001:2009: pha gu dra phyed mda' yab pu shus mdzes //
NK105(be)001:2010: phyur bu'i thod pa rin chen rdo rje'i tog /
NK105(be)001:2011: dur khrod brgyad kyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor dbus //
NK105(be)001:2012: seng ge glang chen rta dang rma bya dang //
NK105(be)001:2013: shang shang pad+ma nyi zlas spras pa'i steng //
NK105(be)001:2014: rigs lnga so so'i yum dang sems dpa' brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2015: sems ma brgyad dang sgo ba yab yum brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2016: thub pa drug rnams so so'i gnas bzhugs te //
NK105(be)001:2017: sku mdog phyag mtshan rgyan rnams rdzogs pa las //
NK105(be)001:2018: mu med 'od zer phyogs mtha' gtugs par 'phro //
NK105(be)001:2019: gtso bo'i thugs kar gzhi yi kun du bzang //
NK105(be)001:2020: yab yum 'khril sbyor mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2021: mkha' ltar dri med mthon mthing skyil krung tshul //
NK105(be)001:2022: tshon gang 'od kyi gong bu 'bar bar bsgom //
NK105(be)001:2023: de las 'od 'phros snang srid snod bcud sbyangs //
NK105(be)001:2024: thams cad rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2025: yi ge gsum dang rigs lnga'i sa bon bzlas //
NK105(be)001:2026: grag stong skye med brag ca ji bzhin no //
NK105(be)001:2027: de nyid ngang la ma bcos mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2028: rang sems ye nas lha yi rang bzhin la //
NK105(be)001:2029: lus ni dkyil 'khor sgra tshig gsang sngags nyid //
NK105(be)001:2030: thams cad lhun rdzogs ye shes chen po'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2031: dam tshig ye shes gnyis med dgug gzhug med //
NK105(be)001:2032: gshegs gsol mi dgos bzang ngan blang dor med //
NK105(be)001:2033: ye nas dkyil 'khor yin pa'i bdag nyid la //
NK105(be)001:2034: yin par shes pa'i tshul gyis gsal 'debs las //
NK105(be)001:2035: ma grub pa la yang grub byed pa min //
NK105(be)001:2036: rjes la zhen pa yod na rim gyis bsdu //
NK105(be)001:2037: gang du'ang mi dmigs spros dang bral bar gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2038: med na sgyu ma chu zla'i ngang nyid nas //
NK105(be)001:2039: dge ba sems can don du bsngo bar bya //
NK105(be)001:2040: spyod lam kun du stong gsal sgyu ma'i tshul //
NK105(be)001:2041: snang dang grag pa thams cad lha dang sngags //
NK105(be)001:2042: dran dang sems pa thams cad ye shes su //
NK105(be)001:2043: skad cig skad cig ma yengs shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2044: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig gtsang ma bsrung //
NK105(be)001:2045: shes dang mi spang spyad dang dang du blang //
NK105(be)001:2046: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga lnga ste //
NK105(be)001:2047: nyi shu rtsa lnga mdor bsdus sku gsung thugs //
NK105(be)001:2048: de yang rang sems rnam dag tshul la bslab //
NK105(be)001:2049: nya dang gnam stong tshes brgyad nyi shu dgu //
NK105(be)001:2050: tshes bcu yar ngo mar ngo'i nyin dang mtshan //
NK105(be)001:2051: bsnyen sgrub tshogs mchod bskang bshags 'bad par bya //
NK105(be)001:2052: rlung sems rtsa dang thig le'i rnal 'byor sogs //
NK105(be)001:2053: yang zab gnad la nan tan snying por bya //
NK105(be)001:2054: bde gsal mi rtog zung 'jug lam bsgoms pas //
NK105(be)001:2055: rdo rje 'dzin pa tshe 'dir rdzogs sangs rgya //
NK105(be)001:2056: de ltar rab gsang bla med snying po 'dis //
NK105(be)001:2057: he ru ka dpal grong du nyer 'tsho zhing //
NK105(be)001:2058: 'gro kun las dang nyon mongs srid pa 'dir //
NK105(be)001:2059: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:2060: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:2061: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o////de ltar bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel rnal 'byor pas //
NK105(be)001:2062: chos rnams ma skyes stong pa'i tshul la 'jug /
NK105(be)001:2063: de yang snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams kun //
NK105(be)001:2064: ye nas bdag med spros dang bral ba la //
NK105(be)001:2065: ma rig 'dzin pas srid pa 'dir 'khyams te //
NK105(be)001:2066: 'khor 'das bde sdug sna tshogs snang mod kyang //
NK105(be)001:2067: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin stong pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2068: sgyu ma rmi lam 'dra bar mkhyen par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:2069: 'di ltar phyi rol snang ba'i dngos po kun //
NK105(be)001:2070: sems la snang yang sems su grub pa med //
NK105(be)001:2071: sems las gzhan du'ang grub pa 'ga' med de //
NK105(be)001:2072: bag chags dbang gis gzung 'dzin gnyis snang yang //
NK105(be)001:2073: snang dus nyid nas gzung 'dzin gnyis med pa //
NK105(be)001:2074: bzhin dang me long nang gi gzugs bzhin no //
NK105(be)001:2075: der ni byad nyid snang yang ma grub la //
NK105(be)001:2076: byad las gzhan gyi rnam pa btod byed med //
NK105(be)001:2077: med bzhin gnyis su snang ba mngon sum ltar //
NK105(be)001:2078: sna tshogs chos rnams de bzhin shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2079: ma brtags nyams dga' brtags na ngos gzung med //
NK105(be)001:2080: shin tu brtags na smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK105(be)001:2081: yod med mi dmigs mtha' bral ma bral med //
NK105(be)001:2082: sgyu ma'i tshul du skye sogs snang na yang //
NK105(be)001:2083: snang dus nyid nas skye sogs rang bzhin med //
NK105(be)001:2084: smig rgyu'i chu dang rdzing bu'i zla gzugs bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2085: khyad par ma dag 'gro drug snang ba 'di //
NK105(be)001:2086: med bzhin snang ba bag chags 'khrul pa'i gzugs //
NK105(be)001:2087: rab rib can la skra shad snang ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2088: de bsal 'dod pas bad kan sbyong ba ltar //
NK105(be)001:2089: 'khrul snang dag 'dod ma rig ling tog bsal //
NK105(be)001:2090: de yi gnyen por rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK105(be)001:2091: 'khor ba'i bag chags stong par la bzla zhing //
NK105(be)001:2092: stong pa'i rang bzhin snang bar thag bcad de //
NK105(be)001:2093: snang stong gnyis med bden pa gnyis don shes //
NK105(be)001:2094: mtha' gnyis gnas bsal dbu mar bslabs pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2095: srid zhir mi gnas nam mkha'i ngang du grol //
NK105(be)001:2096: 'di ni nges don snying po'i dam pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2097: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs yin //
NK105(be)001:2098: snang ba'i dngos kyis phan gnod gnyis su med //
NK105(be)001:2099: der 'dzin zhen pas srid par 'ching bas na //
NK105(be)001:2100: sna tshogs snang la brtag dpyad mi dgos kyi //
NK105(be)001:2101: 'dzin pa'i sems kyi rtsa ba bcad par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:2102: sems ni snang la rang bzhin 'ga' med de //
NK105(be)001:2103: btsal bas mi rnyed bltas pas mthong ba med //
NK105(be)001:2104: kha dog dbyibs med ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK105(be)001:2105: phyi dang nang med dus gsum skye 'gag med //
NK105(be)001:2106: phyogs dang ris med gzhi rtsa dngos po med //
NK105(be)001:2107: 'di zhes mi mtshon bsam yul 'das pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2108: 'gags pa mi dmigs ma skyes phyogs na med //
NK105(be)001:2109: da ltar mi gnas rang bzhin mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2110: sems kyis sems ma tshol bar dal du chug /
NK105(be)001:2111: dgag sgrub dran rig skad cig yid kyi yul //
NK105(be)001:2112: snang tsam nyid nas phyi dang nang na'ang med //
NK105(be)001:2113: btsal bya'i don gyis tshol mkhan byas pas bslad //
NK105(be)001:2114: rang gis rang btsal nam yang rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2115: ye nas skye med rang bzhin gnyug ma'i don //
NK105(be)001:2116: mi gnas 'gag pa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK105(be)001:2117: dus gsum gzhi rtsa med pas stong pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2118: sna tshogs 'char gzhi ma 'gags snang ba la //
NK105(be)001:2119: dngos po mtshan ma med pas rtag pa med //
NK105(be)001:2120: rang shar 'gag pa med pas chad pa med //
NK105(be)001:2121: gnyis dang gnyis med med pas brjod du med //
NK105(be)001:2122: 'di zhes grub pa med pas ngos gzung med //
NK105(be)001:2123: rang bzhin gdod nas dag par shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2124: brtags pas med ltar ma brtags dus na'ang med //
NK105(be)001:2125: rang bzhin gnyis med gdod ma'i ngo bo la //
NK105(be)001:2126: bzang ngan blang dor re dogs mi dmigs pas //
NK105(be)001:2127: brtag dang dpyad pas 'di la ci byar yod //
NK105(be)001:2128: dus gsum yid kyis tshol khro ma byed zhog /
NK105(be)001:2129: rtog ge spros pa'i spun pas bskyod pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2130: rnam g.yeng rlung ltar g.yo bas mi rtogs kyi //
NK105(be)001:2131: bsal gzhag 'gro 'ong med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK105(be)001:2132: kun byed ye shes dri med ngo bo nyid //
NK105(be)001:2133: ji bzhin bzhag pas de bzhin mthong ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2134: 'dir ni sna tshogs grub mtha' mang po dang //
NK105(be)001:2135: bsam brjod rtog pa du mas ci zhig bya //
NK105(be)001:2136: nges pa'i don la grub dang ma grub med //
NK105(be)001:2137: mtha' dang dbus med theg pa'i rnam dbye med //
NK105(be)001:2138: mkha' bzhin rnam dag rgya chad phyogs lhung med //
NK105(be)001:2139: de la yod med blos brtags 'khrul pas na //
NK105(be)001:2140: brjod du med gang ji ltar bshad du yod //
NK105(be)001:2141: don med gnas la rab tu ngal bar zad //
NK105(be)001:2142: ji ltar mkha' dbus dngas pa'i skyed mos tshal //
NK105(be)001:2143: me tog 'bras mang 'bab chus brgyan pa zhig /
NK105(be)001:2144: mngon du bsams nas de yi rnam dbye dang //
NK105(be)001:2145: mthun phyogs mi mthun phyogs gang rtsod pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2146: gang yang dri med sems nyid dag pa la //
NK105(be)001:2147: bcos bsgyur dri mas nam yang mthong ba med //
NK105(be)001:2148: de la bskyed dang rdzogs pas ci zhig bya //
NK105(be)001:2149: dang ba'i bsam gtan bsgoms pas bslad par zad //
NK105(be)001:2150: gdod nas rang bzhin dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK105(be)001:2151: spang gnyen bral thob med kyis dmigs gtad shol //
NK105(be)001:2152: phyi nang gzung 'dzin med kyis ched 'dzin thong //
NK105(be)001:2153: 'di zhes ngos gzung med kyis zhen pa chod //
NK105(be)001:2154: thob dang ma thob med kyis re dogs spongs //
NK105(be)001:2155: gzhi nas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i rig pa la //
NK105(be)001:2156: sna tshogs rkyen gyi rnam pa ci shar yang //
NK105(be)001:2157: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK105(be)001:2158: chu dang rlabs bzhin chos skur phyam gcig go //
NK105(be)001:2159: gang du bltas tshe blta mkhan ngo bo stor //
NK105(be)001:2160: btsal bas ma rnyed yul dang phyogs na med //
NK105(be)001:2161: 'tshol mkhan nyid kyang mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2162: byed po mi gnas bya ba'i yul gyis stong //
NK105(be)001:2163: mkha' bzhin dri med gdod ma'i ngang du phyin //
NK105(be)001:2164: ldog pa'i gnas med da ni gang du 'gro //
NK105(be)001:2165: zad par thug ste 'ong ba 'ga' yang med //
NK105(be)001:2166: sus kyang mi mthong kho bo gang na 'dug /
NK105(be)001:2167: de nyid shes na gzhan zhig dgos mi 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2168: grol ba rnams ni nga bzhin 'khrul pa chad //
NK105(be)001:2169: da ni mi 'dri sems kyi gzhi rtsa stor //
NK105(be)001:2170: gtad med 'dzin med nges med 'di yin med //
NK105(be)001:2171: phyal ba lhug pa yengs pa phyam gcig pa //
NK105(be)001:2172: 'di ltar rtogs nas da ni glu len te //
NK105(be)001:2173: dri med 'od zer shar bas bstan nas song //
NK105(be)001:2174: kye ho grogs dag snang ba'i yul la ltos //
NK105(be)001:2175: thams cad ma skyes stong par mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2176: me long gzugs brnyan sna tshogs ci shar yang //
NK105(be)001:2177: me long ngos yin dngas par gcig pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2178: de nyid 'byed pa'i yid la tshur ltos dang //
NK105(be)001:2179: sems ni mkha' 'dra dgag sgrub kun dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2180: mkha' la sprin rnams byung nas zhig na yang //
NK105(be)001:2181: nam mkha'i cho 'phrul gnyis med dag pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2182: rang bzhin dri med gdod ma'i sangs rgyas te //
NK105(be)001:2183: ma byas lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2184: yul sems gnyis med ye nas dag pa la //
NK105(be)001:2185: spang blang gnyis med phyogs ris dgag sgrub med //
NK105(be)001:2186: gang snang bden med gang shar stong pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2187: thams cad mnyam nyid gza' gtad kun dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2188: yul la nges med snang ba sna tshogs ltar //
NK105(be)001:2189: blo la gtad med phyogs bral chen po nyid //
NK105(be)001:2190: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2191: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams la //
NK105(be)001:2192: 'das pa'i chos rnams mi dmigs mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2193: ma 'ongs chos rnams ma skyes mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2194: da lta'i chos rnams mi gnas mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2195: dus gsum dus med gzhi bral mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2196: thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2197: snang srid 'khor 'das sems kyi gzugs brnyan te //
NK105(be)001:2198: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK105(be)001:2199: nam mkha'i rang bzhin dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med //
NK105(be)001:2200: 'gyur med rang bzhin gzod nas mya ngan 'das //
NK105(be)001:2201: gzhi nas byang chub kun du bzang po yin //
NK105(be)001:2202: snang dang stong pa dbyer med gdod ma'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2203: gcig dang du mar mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2204: phyogs dang ris med thams cad mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2205: snang mnyam stong mnyam bden mnyam brdzun par mnyam //
NK105(be)001:2206: yod mnyam med mnyam mtha' las 'das par mnyam //
NK105(be)001:2207: dbyings gcig gdod nas dag pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2208: blo yis brtags pa thams cad ngo bos stong //
NK105(be)001:2209: ming rnams glo bur rang mtshan sgro btags nyid //
NK105(be)001:2210: bden brdzun gnyis med yul sems 'brel pa med //
NK105(be)001:2211: gcig gis gcig la ma gos gzung 'dzin med //
NK105(be)001:2212: ji ltar me long gzugs bzhin snang ba ni //
NK105(be)001:2213: yul gyi rnam pa dbang po'i shes la shar //
NK105(be)001:2214: de nyid bzung bas chags sdang srid par 'khrul //
NK105(be)001:2215: nan tar gtugs ni sems ni ma 'phos shing //
NK105(be)001:2216: yul gyi rnam pa'ang sems la shar ba med //
NK105(be)001:2217: ngo bo med phyir gnyis su ma grub bo //
NK105(be)001:2218: yul rnams thams cad rang bzhin med par gcig /
NK105(be)001:2219: blo rnams thams cad ngos gzung med par gcig /
NK105(be)001:2220: snang sems gnyis med gdod nas dag par gcig /
NK105(be)001:2221: brtag dpyad mi dgos gzhi nas grol bar gcig /'khor 'das gnyis med sems kyi ngang du gcig /
NK105(be)001:2222: chu bo sna tshogs rgya mtsho'i ngang du gcig /
NK105(be)001:2223: thams cad ro mnyam lhan cig skyes par gcig /'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur nam mkha'i ngang du gcig /
NK105(be)001:2224: sems kyi dgag sgrub stong pa'i ngang du gcig /
NK105(be)001:2225: gang shar rang grol gnyis med dag par gcig /
NK105(be)001:2226: dba' rlabs rol pa chu bo'i ngang du gcig /
NK105(be)001:2227: de ltar rtogs na skyes bu mkhas pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2228: sna tshogs ngos gzung med pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK105(be)001:2229: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK105(be)001:2230: bzang ngan blang dor med pa'i rol pa la //
NK105(be)001:2231: blo yis gnyis su ma 'dzin gang bder zhog /
NK105(be)001:2232: gtad med yul la nges med snang ba shar //
NK105(be)001:2233: 'dzin med rig pa rnam yin chen po ni //
NK105(be)001:2234: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs yin //
NK105(be)001:2235: de ltar chos kun mnyam pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK105(be)001:2236: blo bral ngang du 'dzin med la bzlas nas //
NK105(be)001:2237: phyogs bral rig pa khol bur bcings pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2238: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:2239: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:2240: gzhi rtogs pa'i shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas
NK105(be)001:2241: pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o////de ltar chos kun mnyam pa'i
NK105(be)001:2242: don mthong nas // gnas lugs ngang la ji bzhin gzhag pa gces //
NK105(be)001:2243: de yang dbang po'i rim pas bstan pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2244: dbang po yang rab gnas lugs rtogs pas grol //
NK105(be)001:2245: sgom dang bsgom bya gnyis med don mthong nas //
NK105(be)001:2246: snang srid gzhi grol sems nyid bya btsal med //
NK105(be)001:2247: phyogs bral rig pa chu bo'i rgyun bzhin 'char //
NK105(be)001:2248: thun mtshams ris med 'di yin nges gzung med //
NK105(be)001:2249: thams cad rang grol kun du bzang po'i zhing //
NK105(be)001:2250: rtags dang tshad med rang byung gzhi klong yangs //
NK105(be)001:2251: ji bzhin ngang la ye bzhin gnas pas na //
NK105(be)001:2252: gol dang gol sa rtsal sbyong bogs 'byin med //
NK105(be)001:2253: thob dang ma thob med par thag chod pas //
NK105(be)001:2254: 'bras bur smon med da lta rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK105(be)001:2255: de 'dra'i rnal 'byor nam mkha' rab 'byams yin //
NK105(be)001:2256: 'bring dang tha mas goms la brtson dgos te //
NK105(be)001:2257: ji srid bdag 'dzin dbyings su ma nub par //
NK105(be)001:2258: de srid sna tshogs thabs kyis bsgom par bya //
NK105(be)001:2259: khyad par rnam rtog ngan pas srid par 'khrid //
NK105(be)001:2260: de nyid grol phyir bsam gtan thabs la brten //
NK105(be)001:2261: phyi nas shes rab mtha' grol klong yangs 'char //
NK105(be)001:2262: zhi gnas kyis ni nyon mongs mgo gnon la //
NK105(be)001:2263: lhag mthong gis ni nyon mongs rtsa ba 'byin //
NK105(be)001:2264: des na rab kyis ngan rtog chos skur lhongs //
NK105(be)001:2265: bzang ngan med na gnyen po bsgom mi dgos //
NK105(be)001:2266: 'bring gis ngang dngas zung 'brel bsgoms pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2267: bzang ngan rtog pa dbyings su nub gyur nas //
NK105(be)001:2268: zung 'brel rtogs pa nam mkha' lta bu 'char //
NK105(be)001:2269: tha mas thog mar zhi gnas btsal ba yis //
NK105(be)001:2270: gang dmigs de la brtan pa thob par sla //
NK105(be)001:2271: de nas lhag mthong so sor rtog bsgoms pas //
NK105(be)001:2272: phyi nang snang sems gzhi grol chen por 'char //
NK105(be)001:2273: des na dbang po'i rim pa shes pa gces //
NK105(be)001:2274: da ni dbang po 'bring gi sgom pa bstan //
NK105(be)001:2275: ji ltar chu ni dba' rlabs rnyog pa na //
NK105(be)001:2276: dngas pa'i gzugs brnyan mi gsal g.yo ba ltar //
NK105(be)001:2277: yid ni mi bsrun kun rtog 'phyar zhing g.yo //
NK105(be)001:2278: sna tshogs spros la kun du 'chel ba na //
NK105(be)001:2279: sems nyid 'od gsal dngas pa'i ye shes dang //
NK105(be)001:2280: spyan dang mngon shes gza' skar mi 'char bas //
NK105(be)001:2281: gcig tu mi g.yo mnyam par gzhag pa gces //
NK105(be)001:2282: lus ni chos bdun ri rgyal lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2283: dbang po mtha' bral rdzing bu'i gza' skar 'dra //
NK105(be)001:2284: sems nyid stong gsal dngas pa'i nam mkha' bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2285: bying rgod gnyis med spros dang bral bar gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2286: de tshe rang bzhin gcig ste gdod ma'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2287: gzung dang 'dzin pa mi dmigs chos kyi sku //
NK105(be)001:2288: dri med 'od gsal nyi ma'i snying po ni //
NK105(be)001:2289: bde gsal mi rtog mtha' dbus med pa 'char //
NK105(be)001:2290: snang dang stong pa thams cad phyam gcig la //
NK105(be)001:2291: yod dang med pa kun gyi mtha' las 'das //
NK105(be)001:2292: srid dang zhi ba gnyis su mi rtog pa //
NK105(be)001:2293: shes dang shes bya gcig pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK105(be)001:2294: mnyam dang mi mnyam med pa'i chos nyid mthong //
NK105(be)001:2295: 'di ni 'phags pa'i bden mthong ye shes rgyu //
NK105(be)001:2296: phyi nas de bzhin nyid mthong blo mig gis //
NK105(be)001:2297: rgyal ba'i chos sku phun tshogs bsgrub pas na //
NK105(be)001:2298: skal bzang rnams kyis rtag tu mnyam par zhog /
NK105(be)001:2299: sems nyid ma skyes mkha' ltar dag pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2300: sems byung mi dmigs sprin tshogs dengs pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2301: yeng med spros dang bral ba'i shes pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2302: ji bzhin ngang la ye bzhin mnyam par shog /
NK105(be)001:2303: dngas shing stongs pa rgya mtsho lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2304: gzung 'dzin rnyog bral dba' rlabs med par zhog /
NK105(be)001:2305: stong zhing gsal ba nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2306: kun rtog sprin med phyogs lhung bral bar zhog /
NK105(be)001:2307: brtan zhing mi g.yo ri rgyal lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2308: dgag sgrub gnyis med re dogs bral bar zhog /
NK105(be)001:2309: dag cing gsal ba me long lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2310: snang yul ma 'gags gzugs brnyan lta bur zhog /
NK105(be)001:2311: ye grol sor gzhag 'ja' tshon lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2312: bying rgod gnyis med dag cing gsal bar zhog /
NK105(be)001:2313: gzhan du ma yengs mda' mkhan lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2314: gnyug ma'i ye shes spro bsdu bral bar zhog /
NK105(be)001:2315: thag chod shes pa las zin lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2316: re dogs gnyis med lhun gyis grub par shog /'di ni rang bzhin dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:2317: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2318: skye med ngang der gnas pas zhi gnas la //
NK105(be)001:2319: gsal stong spros dang bral bas lhag mthong nyid //
NK105(be)001:2320: dbyer med ngo bo gcig pas zung du 'brel //
NK105(be)001:2321: de tshe zab zhi spros dang bral ba'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2322: smra bsam brjod du med pa'i don mthong bas //
NK105(be)001:2323: snang ba'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK105(be)001:2324: 'od gsal shes rab pha rol phyin zhes bya //
NK105(be)001:2325: de nyid mthong bas sems ni rab zhi zhing //
NK105(be)001:2326: phyi nang chos la dgag sgrub zhen pa chung //
NK105(be)001:2327: stong pa'i ngang nas snying rje phyogs med 'char //
NK105(be)001:2328: rang gzhan don du dge la spyod cing bskul //
NK105(be)001:2329: dben par dga' zhing rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi nyung //
NK105(be)001:2330: rmi lam na yang dge ba'i chos la spyod //
NK105(be)001:2331: des ni thar pa'i lam sna zin pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2332: de nas ches cher gong du goms pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2333: sems gsal ye shes sngon pas rgya che zhing //
NK105(be)001:2334: snang ba rmi lam sgyu mar rab tu rtogs //
NK105(be)001:2335: chos rnams gnyis med ngang du ro gcig pas //
NK105(be)001:2336: skyes dang ma skyes med par mthong ba'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:2337: mched pa'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK105(be)001:2338: bsam gtan dga' bas brgyan pa thob pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2339: de tshe lus sems sngon pas rab dag cing //
NK105(be)001:2340: thabs dang shes rab dri med rtogs pa 'char //
NK105(be)001:2341: mngon shes ldan zhing snying rjes phan pa 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2342: srid la skyo bas sems ni nges par 'byung //
NK105(be)001:2343: rmi lam na yang chos kun de 'drar rtogs //
NK105(be)001:2344: lus kyi phyi nang shig sro 'bu srin med //
NK105(be)001:2345: bying rgod bral zhing nyin mtshan ting 'dzin 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2346: skye bo des ni 'phags lam myur du mthong //
NK105(be)001:2347: de nas ches cher goms pas sngon pas lhag /
NK105(be)001:2348: ting 'dzin rtogs pa'i nyi ma sngon med 'char //
NK105(be)001:2349: chos kun tshul gcig mnyam pa'i don mthong nas //
NK105(be)001:2350: spyan dang mngon shes sgrib pa med mnga' bas //
NK105(be)001:2351: zhing khams brgya stong bye ba dpag med mthong //
NK105(be)001:2352: de tshe zag med 'phags pa'i ye shes te //
NK105(be)001:2353: thob pa zhes bya mngon du gyur pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2354: de las ches cher gong du 'phel ba yis //
NK105(be)001:2355: rtogs pa'i ting 'dzin yon tan grangs med cing //
NK105(be)001:2356: rtog dang mi rtog mnyam pa'i chos nyid las //
NK105(be)001:2357: gzungs sprin ye shes dri med rgya che zhing //
NK105(be)001:2358: mnyam par gzhag dang ma bzhag gnyis med par //
NK105(be)001:2359: rtag tu mnyam gzhag sprul pa bsam yas ston //
NK105(be)001:2360: tshad med zhing dang ye shes gzigs pa 'jug /
NK105(be)001:2361: rtsa khams dag cing rlung sems yon tan mchog /
NK105(be)001:2362: shin tu rgya che dri ma med pa na //
NK105(be)001:2363: nye bar thob pa zhes bya'i ye shes te //
NK105(be)001:2364: 'phags lam rdzogs nas myur du byang chub 'thob //
NK105(be)001:2365: 'di ni 'od gsal snying po'i theg pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2366: skal bzang 'bras bu tshe 'dir grol ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2367: dbang po tha mas bsgom pa'i rim pa yang //
NK105(be)001:2368: dang por zhi lhag so sor rtsal sbyang ste //
NK105(be)001:2369: brtan par gyur nas zung 'jug dbyer med bsgom //
NK105(be)001:2370: de yang thabs tshul dpag med tshul la bslab //
NK105(be)001:2371: thog mar zhi gnas btsal ba'i rim pa ni //
NK105(be)001:2372: dben pa'i phyogs su stan la rab 'dug nas //
NK105(be)001:2373: dbugs dbyung barnguba pa'i kha dog grangs rnams kyis //
NK105(be)001:2374: nyin 'gar rnam rtog 'dul zhing gnas par bya //
NK105(be)001:2375: de nas byams sogs bzhi dang sems gnyis dang //
NK105(be)001:2376: bskyed rim ngang ni bris sku glegs bam sogs //
NK105(be)001:2377: dge ba'i yul ni gang yang rung zhig la //
NK105(be)001:2378: dmigs pa rtse gcig ma yengs mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2379: de ltar bzhag pas sems ni las rung zhing //
NK105(be)001:2380: gzhan du mi 'phro gar gtad yul la zin //
NK105(be)001:2381: ji tsam bzhag pa de tsam mnyam par gnas //
NK105(be)001:2382: lus ngag sems ni dga' bdes khyab pa na //
NK105(be)001:2383: rtse gcig mi g.yo'i zhi gnas grub pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2384: de nas lhag mthong don la bslab pa ni //
NK105(be)001:2385: phyi rol snang srid 'khor 'das chos 'di rnams //
NK105(be)001:2386: sna tshogs snang bas rmi lam sgyu 'dra zhing //
NK105(be)001:2387: gzugs brnyan sprul pa sgra brnyan dri za'i grong //
NK105(be)001:2388: mig yor smig rgyu 'dra zhing snying po med //
NK105(be)001:2389: snang bas stong ste rang bzhin stong pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2390: thams cad nam mkha' 'dra zhing bdag med pas //
NK105(be)001:2391: skye med spros dang bral bar mnyam pa bzhag /
NK105(be)001:2392: de yis phyi rol chos la bdag med cing //
NK105(be)001:2393: gzung dang gzung yul rang bzhin med par rtogs //
NK105(be)001:2394: de nas nang gi sems la 'di ltar brtag /
NK105(be)001:2395: sna tshogs rtog la ngo bo med pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2396: dgag sgrub bden brdzun bde sdug btang snyoms sogs //
NK105(be)001:2397: yul la 'phro zhing ngos gzung med pa khyod //
NK105(be)001:2398: dang po gang 'ongs da lta gang na gnas //
NK105(be)001:2399: tha ma gar 'gro dbyibs dang kha dog ci //
NK105(be)001:2400: snyam du brtags tshe 'di ltar mthong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2401: sems ni dang por skye ba'i rgyus stong zhing //
NK105(be)001:2402: bar du gnas dang tha mar 'gag pas stong //
NK105(be)001:2403: kha dog dbyibs med ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK105(be)001:2404: 'das pa 'gags shing ma 'ongs ma skyes la //
NK105(be)001:2405: da lta mi gnas phyi nang gang na'ang med //
NK105(be)001:2406: nam mkha' 'dra zhing spros dang bral bar shes //
NK105(be)001:2407: de tshe sems la gang yang mi bsam par //
NK105(be)001:2408: chad pa ngal gso bzhin du lhod kyis glod //
NK105(be)001:2409: ci yang mi bsam yid la byed pa bor //
NK105(be)001:2410: thams cad gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang la gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2411: de yis ngar 'dzin gang zag bdag med cing //
NK105(be)001:2412: 'dzin pa'i sems la rang bzhin med par rtogs //
NK105(be)001:2413: de nas zung 'jug gnyug ma'i ye shes ni //
NK105(be)001:2414: snang sems gnyis med chu dang chu zla bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2415: gnyis su gzung bas srid par 'khrul na yang //
NK105(be)001:2416: gnyis med shes pas mya ngan 'das zhir 'gro //
NK105(be)001:2417: de bas gnyis med don la 'di ltar bslab //
NK105(be)001:2418: chos rnams ma skyes sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK105(be)001:2419: sems kyi rang bzhin dag cing dri ma med //
NK105(be)001:2420: dri med stong gsal spros dang bral bar gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2421: de yis nyon mongs rnyog pa rab zhi zhing //
NK105(be)001:2422: rnam par mi rtog ye shes chen por gnas //
NK105(be)001:2423: rig dang mngon shes ting 'dzin 'grub 'gyur zhing //
NK105(be)001:2424: gzung 'dzin gnyis med mtha' bral dbu mar rtogs //
NK105(be)001:2425: de tshe sems ni nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK105(be)001:2426: yul ni mi dmigs rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2427: sgom dang bsgom bya med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK105(be)001:2428: bya rgyu byed mkhan med pas gdod ma'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2429: dri med rang bzhin dag pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK105(be)001:2430: gzung yul mi dmigs chu zla mig yor la //
NK105(be)001:2431: 'dzin mkhan mi dmigs g.yo med phyogs lhung bral //
NK105(be)001:2432: snang sems gnyis med pha rol phyin pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2433: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK105(be)001:2434: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos nyid khong du chud //
NK105(be)001:2435: 'dzin med yangs pa'i ting 'dzin gru chen gyis //
NK105(be)001:2436: srid gsum rgya mtsho'i pha rol brgal bas na //
NK105(be)001:2437: gzhi bde'i steng du blo bde rgyun mi 'chad //
NK105(be)001:2438: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du phyin //
NK105(be)001:2439: gnas pas zhi gnas chos sku stong pa la //
NK105(be)001:2440: gsal bas lhag mthong gzugs sku snang ba nyid //
NK105(be)001:2441: thabs dang shes rab tshogs gnyis bskyed rdzogs grub //
NK105(be)001:2442: lhag mthong rtogs pa'i shes rab bskyed byas nas //
NK105(be)001:2443: zhi gnas kyis ni de yi ngang la gnas //
NK105(be)001:2444: gang tshe gzung 'dzin dngos dang dngos med du //
NK105(be)001:2445: blo yi rnam par rab tu mi gnas pa //
NK105(be)001:2446: de tshe dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med par //
NK105(be)001:2447: sems dang sems byung dmigs pa med par zhi //
NK105(be)001:2448: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK105(be)001:2449: gnas skabs glo bur kun rtog dag pa na //
NK105(be)001:2450: snyoms 'jug dgu dang rdzu 'phrul mngon shes 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2451: ting 'dzin grangs med gzugs sprin lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2452: rang sa 'dod pa'i sems gang rtse gcig pa //
NK105(be)001:2453: de las rtog dang dpyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:2454: dga' bde'i yan lag bsam gtan dang po skye //
NK105(be)001:2455: de las rtog med dpyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:2456: sems gsal dga' bde'i rang bzhin gnyis pa skye //
NK105(be)001:2457: de las rtog dpyod gnyis med ting nge 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:2458: dga' bdes brlan pa'i yan lag gsum pa skye //
NK105(be)001:2459: de las dga' ba sdud pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK105(be)001:2460: bzhi pa phan yon yan lag bcas pa skye //
NK105(be)001:2461: de las mkha' ltar dag cing dngas pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2462: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2463: de las chos kun sems nyid spros pa med //
NK105(be)001:2464: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2465: de las snang sems mi dmigs spros dang bral //
NK105(be)001:2466: ci yang med pa'i skye mched 'grub par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2467: de las yod med spros kun bral ba'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2468: yod min med min skye mched 'grub par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2469: de las sna tshogs nyon mongs spros pa'i sems //
NK105(be)001:2470: rang bzhin 'gog pa zhi ba thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2471: de ltar mthar gyis snyoms 'jug dgu po yang //
NK105(be)001:2472: rim dang rim min thod rgal rtsal sbyangs pas //
NK105(be)001:2473: rang gzhan snga phyi'i tshe rabs las rnams dang //
NK105(be)001:2474: sems kyi spyod yul gang yin shes pa dang //
NK105(be)001:2475: 'chi 'pho skye dang sgrib pas chod kyang mthong //
NK105(be)001:2476: gcig dang du mar rdzu zhing rnam par 'phrul //
NK105(be)001:2477: nyon mongs med cing ji snyed ji bzhin shes //
NK105(be)001:2478: zhing rnams bde gshegs sras kyis gang ba mthong //
NK105(be)001:2479: de tshe snang ba sgyu mar rab rtogs pas //
NK105(be)001:2480: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin nyid dang ni //
NK105(be)001:2481: sems kyi gdung bral rnyog pa rab zhi'i phyir //
