NK105(be)001:2482: zla ba dri ma med pa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK105(be)001:2483: chos kun mi dmigs mnyam pa'i ngang gcig pas //
NK105(be)001:2484: mkha' ltar gos pa med pa'i ting 'dzin sogs //
NK105(be)001:2485: brgya stong grangs med rab tu 'grub par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2486: lhag mthong gis ni rab tu rtogs pa'i don //
NK105(be)001:2487: zhi gnas dam pas rtse gcig gzung ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:2488: gzungs dang ting 'dzin zung 'brel lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2489: lam lnga'i rim pa bgrod las grol ba ste //
NK105(be)001:2490: tshogs lam chung ngur lus tshor sems dang chos //
NK105(be)001:2491: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi bsgom zhing //
NK105(be)001:2493: dge dang mi dge'i zhen bzhi yang dag spong //
NK105(be)001:2494: chen por 'dun sems dpyod dang dran pa bzhis //
NK105(be)001:2495: rdzu 'phrul rten 'grub rkang pa bzhi po bsgom //
NK105(be)001:2496: sbyor lam bzhi ste drod dang rtse mo ru //
NK105(be)001:2497: dad brtson dran dang ting 'dzin shes rab kyis //
NK105(be)001:2498: dbang po lnga dang bzod pa chos mchog tu //
NK105(be)001:2499: dad sogs stobs lnga rab tu sgom par byed //
NK105(be)001:2500: mthong ba'i lam ste rab tu dga' ba'i sar //
NK105(be)001:2501: dad brtson dran pa ting 'dzin shes rab dga' //
NK105(be)001:2502: shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi //
NK105(be)001:2503: yan lag bdun po dag ni legs bsgom zhing //
NK105(be)001:2504: sgom lam chung 'bring chen po re re zhing //
NK105(be)001:2505: chung ngu'i chung ngu chung ngu'i 'bring dang ni //
NK105(be)001:2506: chung ngu'i che sogs sa dgu rim pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2507: dri ma med dang 'od byed 'od 'phro can //
NK105(be)001:2508: sbyang dka' mngon gyur ring song mi g.yo ba //
NK105(be)001:2509: legs pa'i blo gros chos kyi sprin rnams su //
NK105(be)001:2510: yang dag lta dang rtog pa ngag dang las //
NK105(be)001:2511: 'tsho rtsol dran pa ting 'dzin 'phags lam brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2512: de ltar byang chub phyogs chos sum cu bdun //
NK105(be)001:2513: slob pa'i lam bzhir bsgoms pa'i mjug thogs su //
NK105(be)001:2514: mi slob sa la mi gnas mya ngan 'da' //
NK105(be)001:2515: de ltar sa dang lam rnams ma bgrod pa'i //
NK105(be)001:2516: sangs rgyas de 'dra nam yang 'byung ba med //
NK105(be)001:2517: bskal mang tshe rabs du ma tshe gang grol //
NK105(be)001:2518: de dag kun kyang lam 'dir brten pas na //
NK105(be)001:2519: rgyu 'bras theg pa gang la zhugs rnams kyis //
NK105(be)001:2520: sa dang lam rnams mkhyen nas bgrod par mdzod //
NK105(be)001:2521: de ltar zab zhi 'od gsal snying po yis //
NK105(be)001:2522: 'gro kun sems kyi rnyog pa rab zhi nas //
NK105(be)001:2523: srid 'dir yun ring spros la 'chel ba yis //
NK105(be)001:2524: dub pa'i sems nyid di ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:2525: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:2526: lam bsam gtan dri ma med pa zhi lhag zung
NK105(be)001:2527: du 'brel ba'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o////de ltar zung
NK105(be)001:2529: ting 'dzin mi g.yo yan lag gsum la bslab //
NK105(be)001:2530: gang gis bsgrub pa cho ga'i yan lag dang //
NK105(be)001:2531: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag dang //
NK105(be)001:2532: gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag go //
NK105(be)001:2533: gang gis bsgrub pa'i skye bo nges 'byung can //
NK105(be)001:2534: lus ni 'du 'dzi'i grong las rgyang bsrings shing //
NK105(be)001:2535: sems ni spros pa'i tshogs las ring du bsrings //
NK105(be)001:2536: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2537: dad ldan ngo tsha shes shing khrel yod la //
NK105(be)001:2538: bag yod tshul khrims dag cing dge la spro //
NK105(be)001:2539: mang thos 'dod pa chung zhing chog shes ldan //
NK105(be)001:2540: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2541: lus sems bsdams shing dben par gnas la dga' //
NK105(be)001:2542: gnyid dang snyom las smra la dga' ba spongs //
NK105(be)001:2543: rgod 'gyod med cing gzhan dang 'dris pa nyung //
NK105(be)001:2544: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2545: grong dang grong 'dab skye bo'i 'du 'dzi med //
NK105(be)001:2546: gnas dang dgon par mang po'i rten 'dris med //
NK105(be)001:2547: don dang bya ba sna tshogs brel ba med //
NK105(be)001:2548: de yis ting 'dzin 'di ni myur du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2549: tshe 'di'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde 'bras dang //
NK105(be)001:2550: rang don zhi ba gnyer min 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:2551: srid las thar 'dod nges 'byung skyo shas can //
NK105(be)001:2552: de yis ting 'dzin mchog 'di myur du 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2553: ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag kyang //
NK105(be)001:2554: gnyid rmugs rgod 'gyod the tshom sgrib pa lnga //
NK105(be)001:2555: spangs te zhi lhag zung 'brel tshul gyis bsgrub //
NK105(be)001:2556: gnyid rmugs gnyis kyis zhi gnas rab tu sgrib //
NK105(be)001:2557: rgod 'gyod gnyis kyis lhag mthong rnam par g.yeng //
NK105(be)001:2558: the tshom gnyis ka'i gnod byed mi mthun phyogs //
NK105(be)001:2559: de ltar lnga nyid bying rgod gnyis su 'du //
NK105(be)001:2560: bying na gseng zhing rgod na rtse gcig bsgom //
NK105(be)001:2561: zhi gnas med pa'i lhag mthong spros la rgod //
NK105(be)001:2562: lhag mthong med pa'i zhi gnas lung ma bstan //
NK105(be)001:2563: zung 'brel sgrib pa'i gnyen po mchog gi lam //
NK105(be)001:2564: zhi gnas lus ngag yid sems dal bas 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2565: de yang chos kun rang bzhin mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2566: dmigs pa rab zhi gtso bo'i yan lag yin //
NK105(be)001:2567: dmigs pa gcig la sems 'dzin 'khor gyi tshul //
NK105(be)001:2568: de yang snang bcas snang med rnam pa gnyis //
NK105(be)001:2569: phyi nang gnyis te bzhi yis zin par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2570: snang bcas gzugs sogs sgo lnga'i yul rnams la //
NK105(be)001:2571: snang med mi rtog rtse gcig ngang la 'jog /
NK105(be)001:2572: phyi rol rdo shing sku gzugs la sogs dang //
NK105(be)001:2573: nang nyid snying gar pad+ma 'thur 'phyang sogs //
NK105(be)001:2574: dmigs yul gcig la rtse gcig sems 'jog pa //
NK105(be)001:2575: zhi gnas bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi yan lag yin //
NK105(be)001:2576: de yis rtse gcig zhi gnas skyes pa'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:2577: spel zhing brtan phyir lhag mthong ye shes spro //
NK105(be)001:2578: bogs 'byin spyod lam kun dang bsre ba gces //
NK105(be)001:2579: stengs na lus sems gsengs la sngar bzhin bsgom //
NK105(be)001:2580: 'dis ni myur du 'grub par 'gyur ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2581: lhag mthong 'dod ces sems gsal dngas pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2582: so sor rtog pa gtso bo'i yan lag la //
NK105(be)001:2583: mi rtog mnyam par 'jog pa 'khor gyi tshul //
NK105(be)001:2584: de yang chos can chos nyid rnam pa gnyis //
NK105(be)001:2585: chos can sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad blta bya zhing //
NK105(be)001:2586: chos nyid mkha' ltar stong pa'i rtsal sbyang bya //
NK105(be)001:2587: ji bzhin ngang la bzhag pas ye shes 'char //
NK105(be)001:2588: stengs na sna tshogs chos la rtsal sbyang ste //
NK105(be)001:2589: sgyu ma stong pa gnyis med dag par blta //
NK105(be)001:2590: 'phro na zhi gnas ngang la mnyam par gzhag /
NK105(be)001:2591: de tshe nam mkha' lta bu'i 'od gsal ni //
NK105(be)001:2592: stong gsal spros dang bral ba'i ngo bo mthong //
NK105(be)001:2593: de yis sgrib gnyis sprin las grol ba 'grub //
NK105(be)001:2594: res 'ga' rgya mtsho lta bu'i 'od gsal 'char //
NK105(be)001:2595: shar grol ngang dngas rtog med lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2596: bogs 'byin spyod lam kun dang de nyid bsre //
NK105(be)001:2597: 'dis ni lhag mthong myur du 'grub par 'gyur //
NK105(be)001:2598: zung 'jug shes pa 'phro gnas mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2599: gnyis kar mi rtog ye shes gtso bo la //
NK105(be)001:2600: yeng med spros dang bral ba 'khor gyi tshul //
NK105(be)001:2601: ji ltar shar gnas de yi ngang bzhag pas //
NK105(be)001:2602: shar bas grol la gnas pas mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)001:2603: zhi lhag zung 'brel bde gsal mi rtog 'char //
NK105(be)001:2604: snang stong thabs shes bskyed rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2605: stengs na zhi lhag so sor rtsal sbyang zhing //
NK105(be)001:2606: bying rgod tshe na ldog la bsgom par bya //
NK105(be)001:2607: bogs 'byin nam mkha' dngas shing sprin med tshe //
NK105(be)001:2608: nyi mar rgyab phyogs mkha' la rab bltas pas //
NK105(be)001:2609: stong gsal shes pa spros dang bral ba 'char //
NK105(be)001:2610: phyi rol dpe yi nam mkha' dag pa las //
NK105(be)001:2611: nang gi chos nyid don gyi nam mkha' che //
NK105(be)001:2612: gsang ba 'od gsal snying po'i nam mkha' ste //
NK105(be)001:2613: nam mkha' sum sprugs dgongs pa shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2614: gnyis med bsgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag ni //
NK105(be)001:2615: thams cad ro mnyam rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2616: spang blang mi bya dmigs gtad zhen pa dor //
NK105(be)001:2617: 'dzin zhen thams cad srid pa'i 'du byed la //
NK105(be)001:2618: dmigs gtad med na mkha' bzhin bcings grol med //
NK105(be)001:2619: ji ltar gzugs brnyan sna tshogs me long ngang //
NK105(be)001:2620: de ltar chos rnams sna tshogs stong pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2621: ji ltar sprin rnams sna tshogs nam mkha'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2622: de bzhin dgag sgrub sna tshogs sems nyid ngang //
NK105(be)001:2623: ji ltar chu bo sna tshogs rgya mtsho'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2624: de bzhin nyams rtogs sna tshogs sgom pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2625: ji ltar sgyu ma sna tshogs sprul pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2626: de bzhin 'khor 'das sna tshogs chos nyid ngang //
NK105(be)001:2627: ji ltar phyogs bcu'i nam mkha' gzhi bral ngang //
NK105(be)001:2628: de bzhin ye grol chos rnams lta ba'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2629: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag gnyis med ngang //
NK105(be)001:2630: de bzhin sems dang sems nyid dbyer med ngang //
NK105(be)001:2631: ji ltar sna tshogs rmi lam gnyid kyi ngang //
NK105(be)001:2632: de bzhin blang dor gnyis med spyod pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2633: ji ltar mtsho dang dba' rlabs chu bo'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2634: de bzhin rtog dang mi rtog mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2635: ji ltar tshong pa don grub bde ba'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2636: de bzhin re dogs gnyis med 'bras bu'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2637: thams cad phyam gcig rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2638: khyab gdal dbyings kyi chos nyid shes par bya //
NK105(be)001:2639: de ltar sna tshogs gnyis med ro gcig gis //
NK105(be)001:2640: 'gro kun bdag gzhan gzung 'dzin las grol te //
NK105(be)001:2641: 'di zhes dmigs pas 'khrul pa'i srid pa 'dir //
NK105(be)001:2642: dub pa'i sems nyid de ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:2643: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:2644: ting nge 'dzin bsgrub pa'i yan lag thabs la mkhas
NK105(be)001:2645: pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o////de ltar thabs dang shes
NK105(be)001:2647: sku dang ye shes phrin las lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2648: sems dang sems byung kun gzhir bcas pa kun //
NK105(be)001:2649: chos kyi dbyings su 'jug pa rab zhi'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:2650: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med ro gcig gyur //
NK105(be)001:2651: de tshe dag pa gnyis ldan spros kun zhi //
NK105(be)001:2652: shin tu skye med 'od gsal snying po'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2653: gnam gang zla ba dbyings su nub pa ltar //
NK105(be)001:2654: phra ba'i ye shes mkha' dbyings pad+mora 'khyil //
NK105(be)001:2655: gang du'ang mi rtog zhi ba brnyes pa'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:2656: chos nyid mi dmigs dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med //
NK105(be)001:2657: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i cha de la //
NK105(be)001:2658: mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku zhes brjod pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2659: gzhi dbyings zad pa'i chos nyid mthar thug pa'o //
NK105(be)001:2660: rang bzhin glo bur sgrib gnyis rnam dag cing //
NK105(be)001:2661: thams cad mkhyen pa'i chos tshul rgya mtsho brnyes //
NK105(be)001:2662: spangs dang rtogs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin pas //
NK105(be)001:2663: stobs sogs pha rol phyin pa'i chas gzhal na //
NK105(be)001:2664: mngon par byang chub sku zhes btags pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2665: ma 'dres yon tan 'char gzhi mthar thug pa'o //
NK105(be)001:2666: shes bya'i yul la de blo mi 'jug cing //
NK105(be)001:2667: shes byed blo la 'dzin pa mi dmigs kyang //
NK105(be)001:2668: nang gsal mkha' dbyings nub pa'i zla ba ltar //
NK105(be)001:2669: thim la ma rmugs phra ba'i ye shes mchog /
NK105(be)001:2670: thams cad mkhyen chas 'char gzhi ngo bo'i tshul //
NK105(be)001:2671: de las gzugs sku rnam mkhyen mched 'gyur zhing //
NK105(be)001:2672: gzhan la snang mdzad yon tan gter yin phyir //
NK105(be)001:2673: shin tu ches phra'i ye shes rab zhi'i chas //
NK105(be)001:2674: zhi ba chos kyi sku zhes rab tu brjod //
NK105(be)001:2675: 'di dag phyi rol yul la mi 'jug cing //
NK105(be)001:2676: chad pa ma yin shin tu phra ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)001:2677: rtag dang chad sogs mu bzhi'i mtha' las 'das //
NK105(be)001:2678: smra bsam brjod med pha rol phyin pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2679: stong pa'i rang bzhin dmigs pa rab zhi bas //
NK105(be)001:2680: rgyal ba rnams las gzhan gyi spyod yul min //
NK105(be)001:2681: chos dbyings pho brang shin tu skye med na //
NK105(be)001:2682: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad rtag bzhugs kyang //
NK105(be)001:2683: gcig gis gcig mi gzigs te chos nyid phyir //
NK105(be)001:2684: rang bzhin zab zhing bzhugs zhes gsungs pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2685: de nyid ngang du rgyal rnams dgongs klong gcig /
NK105(be)001:2686: bum mkha' snga phyi'i nam mkha' gcig pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2687: 'di ni chos nyid stong pa shes rab dang //
NK105(be)001:2688: ye shes tshogs dang rdzogs rim mthar thug pa'o //
NK105(be)001:2689: de nyid ngang las rang snang longs spyod rdzogs //
NK105(be)001:2690: gnas dus ston pa chos 'khor phun tshogs las //
NK105(be)001:2691: gnas ni 'od gsal stug po bkod pa'i zhing //
NK105(be)001:2692: lnga ldan 'od kyis lhun stug gsal zhing 'tsher //
NK105(be)001:2693: 'ja' tshon gdangs gsal nam mkha' gang ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2694: steng 'og phyogs mtshams nam mkha'i dbyings khyab par //
NK105(be)001:2695: gzhal med khang mdzes sgo bzhi rta babs ldan //
NK105(be)001:2696: rtsig pa lnga dang pha gu dra phyed dang //
NK105(be)001:2697: mda' yab pu shu gtsang khang phyur bus mdzes //
NK105(be)001:2698: 'phan gdugs rnga yab dril bu'i phreng ba dang //
NK105(be)001:2699: bla re rgyal mtshan la sogs nam mkha' gang //
NK105(be)001:2700: 'dod yon lha mo mchod pa'i sprin 'phro zhing //
NK105(be)001:2701: 'od zer 'khyil bas phyi nang kun du khyab //
NK105(be)001:2702: dbus dang phyogs bzhi so so'i kha dog la //
NK105(be)001:2703: mthun pa'i rgyan dang kha dog rnam par bkra //
NK105(be)001:2704: che chung ma nges gang bltas de ltar snang //
NK105(be)001:2705: grangs ni tshad med nam mkha'i dbyings kun khyab //
NK105(be)001:2706: ji ltar til gyi gang bu phye ba bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2707: kun gyi nang na seng ge glang chen rta //
NK105(be)001:2708: rma bya shang shang nyi zla pad+mas spras //
NK105(be)001:2709: dus ni ma nges gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur med //
NK105(be)001:2710: dus gsum dus med kun du bzang po'i dus //
NK105(be)001:2711: thams cad mnyam rdzogs chos nyid gdal ba che //
NK105(be)001:2712: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i ngang nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2713: ston pa mtshan rdzogs dpe byad 'bar ba'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2714: rnam snang mi bskyod rin 'byung 'od dpag med //
NK105(be)001:2715: don grub lnga po lnga lngas bskor ba la //
NK105(be)001:2716: nam mkha' dbyings phyug rdo rje m+aa ma k+ai //
NK105(be)001:2717: sangs rgyas spyan dang gos dkar dam tshig sgrol //
NK105(be)001:2718: yab yum mnyam sbyor so so'i rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK105(be)001:2719: mthing ga dkar ser dmar ljang 'od zer 'phro //
NK105(be)001:2720: 'og gzhi zhi ba steng gzhi khro bo'i tshul //
NK105(be)001:2722: he ru ka dpal lnga lngas bskor ba yang //
NK105(be)001:2723: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai lnga dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK105(be)001:2724: de sogs rnam pa brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK105(be)001:2725: chos ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2726: smra bsam brjod du med pa'i klong nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2727: 'khor ni nyid las mi zhan rang snang 'khor //
NK105(be)001:2728: sems dpa' brgyad dang de bzhin sems ma brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2729: sgo ba bzhi dang sgo ma rnam pa bzhi //
NK105(be)001:2730: zhi ba rang bzhin bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las //
NK105(be)001:2731: drug ni gzhan la snang phyir sprul pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2732: gnyis ni dbyings na gnas phyir chos kyi sku //
NK105(be)001:2733: rang snang zhi ba longs sku sum cu bzhi //
NK105(be)001:2734: khyad par 'khor ni nyi shu bzhir gnas so //
NK105(be)001:2735: khro bo'i 'khor ni koo sing phra men brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2736: sgo skyong bzhi dang dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK105(be)001:2737: khro bo rang bzhin lnga bcu rtsa brgyad las //
NK105(be)001:2738: khyad par 'khor ni bzhi bcu brgyad dang bcas //
NK105(be)001:2739: 'bar ba'i cha lugs za byed rngam stabs can //
NK105(be)001:2740: shin tu mi bzad gar dgus rol pa'o //
NK105(be)001:2741: gzhan yang lus grub dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa //
NK105(be)001:2742: de snyed rang snang longs sku'i zhing khams yin //
NK105(be)001:2743: gzhan snang gdul bya'i zhi khro ji snyed pa //
NK105(be)001:2744: sprul skus bsdus phyir rang snang longs sku min //
NK105(be)001:2745: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa rnam lnga'i zhing //
NK105(be)001:2746: thams cad rang snang yin phyir bzang ngan med //
NK105(be)001:2747: kun kyang gsal 'tsher lhun stug 'od zer 'phro //
NK105(be)001:2748: lham me lhan ne lhang nge'i tshul gyis bzhugs //
NK105(be)001:2749: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul te //
NK105(be)001:2750: gcig gis gcig gzigs de yi basngagasa pa brjod //
NK105(be)001:2751: de ltar yid 'ong kun nas bkod pa'i zhing //
NK105(be)001:2752: dag pa'i gdul bya yis kyang mthong mi nus //
NK105(be)001:2753: rang snang stong gzugs bzhin du bsam mi khyab //
NK105(be)001:2754: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi rang snang ngo //
NK105(be)001:2755: de nyid ngang las gdul bya'i 'jig rten du //
NK105(be)001:2756: 'dul byed ston pa rim gyis snang ba ni //
NK105(be)001:2757: rang bzhin 'gro 'dul sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2758: rnam pa gsum gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK105(be)001:2759: de yang rang bzhin sprul sku'i ston pa ni //
NK105(be)001:2760: 'og min mngon dga' dpal ldan pad+ma brtsegs //
NK105(be)001:2761: las rab grub pa'i 'jig rten rnam pa lngar //
NK105(be)001:2762: rnam snang mi bskyod la sogs rigs lnga'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2763: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer 'bar ba la //
NK105(be)001:2764: zhi dang khro tshul dpag med tshul 'chang bas //
NK105(be)001:2765: 'gro ba'i don gnyis lhun gyis grub par mdzad //
NK105(be)001:2766: de yang ye shes lnga lnga'i rang bzhin te //
NK105(be)001:2767: chos dbyings me long mnyam nyid so sor rtog /
NK105(be)001:2768: bya grub ye shes rnam pa lnga po yang //
NK105(be)001:2769: re re'i 'khor du bzhi bzhi ldan pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2770: thams cad ro mnyam gcig gi ngang nyid do //
NK105(be)001:2771: chos dbyings ye shes shin tu mi g.yo ba //
NK105(be)001:2772: gzung 'dzin spros pa'i mtha' las 'das pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2773: me long ye shes gsal stong 'char gzhi'i tshul //
NK105(be)001:2774: ye shes kun gyi 'byung gnas chen po yin //
NK105(be)001:2775: mnyam nyid ye shes chos kun mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK105(be)001:2776: 'khor 'das gnyis med mnyam rdzogs chen po yin //
NK105(be)001:2777: kun rtog ye shes shes bya ma 'dres mkhyen //
NK105(be)001:2778: ji snyed ji bzhin gzigs pa rnam dag yin //
NK105(be)001:2779: bya grub ye shes phrin las phun sum tshogs //
NK105(be)001:2780: shes bya kun la rtag thogs med pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2781: gdul bya'i 'khor ni sa bcu'i sems dpa' la //
NK105(be)001:2782: chos ni ting 'dzin 'od zer rab bkye bas //
NK105(be)001:2783: sa de'i sgrib pa sbyor ba'i blo skyes nas //
NK105(be)001:2784: ser sna la sogs spangs te rgyal la blta //
NK105(be)001:2785: da dung de 'dra'i ston pa rnam dag dang //
NK105(be)001:2786: bdag nyid khyad par mthong nas sgrib pa sbyong //
NK105(be)001:2787: kun du 'od kyi bar du 'god pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2788: gzugs bzang me long bstan pas don mdzad do //
NK105(be)001:2789: dus ni 'gro grol bar du rgyun mi 'chad //
NK105(be)001:2790: longs sku'i zhing na khor mor snang ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2791: de ltar rigs lngar nges pa'i rang bzhin yang //
NK105(be)001:2792: gdul bya gti mug shas cher sbyong ba'i tshe //
NK105(be)001:2793: zhing ni 'og min ston pa rnam snang la //
NK105(be)001:2794: chos ni chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK105(be)001:2795: de bzhin zhe sdang sbyang phyir mi bskyod zhing //
NK105(be)001:2796: nga rgyal rin 'byung 'dod chags 'od dpag med //
NK105(be)001:2797: phrag dog sbyang phyir don grub snang ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2798: de ltar ston pa longs spyod rdzogs na yang //
NK105(be)001:2799: 'khor sogs ston pa nyid las gzhan yin pas //
NK105(be)001:2800: thams cad longs spyod rdzogs min de yi phyir //
NK105(be)001:2801: phyed sprul nyid de rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2802: dag pa'i 'gro ba rnams la snang ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2803: sar gnas rnams las gdul bya gzhan la min //
NK105(be)001:2804: de phyir phyed snang sprul pa'i sku zhes bya //
NK105(be)001:2805: zhing de khod mnyam yid 'ong gzhal med khang //
NK105(be)001:2806: rin chen bdun ldan 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK105(be)001:2807: pad+ma las skyes rgyal sras dpag tu med //
NK105(be)001:2808: longs spyod sna tshogs 'dod dgu'i char pa 'bab //
NK105(be)001:2809: dus bzhir chos gsung dri med g.yer kha'i sgra //
NK105(be)001:2810: dpag bsam rin chen chu mtshos rab tu mdzes //
NK105(be)001:2811: 'di ni zhi ba rang bzhin sprul pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2812: de bzhin khro tshul dkyil 'khor dpag tu med //
NK105(be)001:2813: mkha' 'gro sprin phung 'phro ba'i mkha' spyod gnas //
NK105(be)001:2814: he ru ka dpal rigs lnga'i zhing khams nyid //
NK105(be)001:2815: gsang sngags grub la rab tu snang ba yin //
NK105(be)001:2816: 'di ni ding sang bde chen mkha' spyod ces //
NK105(be)001:2817: mkhas grub rnams la rab tu grags pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2818: de nyid ngang las 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2819: 'gro drug gnas su rang rang ston par snang //
NK105(be)001:2820: de yang brgya byin thags bzangs ris dang ni //
NK105(be)001:2821: sh+aakya thub pa seng ge rab brtan dang //
NK105(be)001:2822: kha 'bar de ba a wa glang mgo ste //
NK105(be)001:2823: thub pa drug gis phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams su //
NK105(be)001:2824: 'gro ba drug gi rgyud drug so sor sbyong //
NK105(be)001:2825: de yang gtso bo'i grangs te sprul pa dang //
NK105(be)001:2826: yang sprul rnams ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste //
NK105(be)001:2827: lha yi gnas su'ang gnas ris so so ru //
NK105(be)001:2828: tshangs dang dbang phyug 'og min bar snyed du //
NK105(be)001:2829: rang rang 'dul byed ston pa'i tshul rnams snang //
NK105(be)001:2830: mi la'ang gang 'dul de la der snang ste //
NK105(be)001:2831: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK105(be)001:2832: rgyal po la sogs sprul nas mi rnams 'dul //
NK105(be)001:2833: lha min gnas su'ang so so'i 'dul byed dang //
NK105(be)001:2834: dud 'gro'i ris su'ang bya la byar snang zhing //
NK105(be)001:2835: ri dgas rnams la seng ge mchog la sogs //
NK105(be)001:2836: so so'i 'dul byed ston pa bsam mi khyab //
NK105(be)001:2837: de bzhin yi dgas dmyal ba'i 'jig rten du //
NK105(be)001:2838: rang rang mthun pa'i gzugs kyis don mdzad do //
NK105(be)001:2839: de ltar 'gro 'dul rnams la ye shes gnyis //
NK105(be)001:2840: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i rnam pa ste //
NK105(be)001:2841: chos nyid dang ni chos can ma 'dres par //
NK105(be)001:2842: so sor mkhyen nas gdul bya'i don gnyis mdzad //
NK105(be)001:2843: ji lta'i ye shes stong pa'i dngos mkhyen nas //
NK105(be)001:2844: 'gro la nye bar zhi ba'i chos ston zhing //
NK105(be)001:2845: ji snyed ye shes sems dang dbang po sogs //
NK105(be)001:2846: ma 'dres mkhyen nas chos tshul bsam yas ston //
NK105(be)001:2847: 'di ni ma dag 'gro la snang ba ste //
NK105(be)001:2848: zhing ni 'gro drug 'jig rten drug rnams su //
NK105(be)001:2849: ston pa 'gro 'dul rang snang mthun pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2850: chos ni ma nges theg pa sna tshogs nyid //
NK105(be)001:2851: dus ni gdul bya'i skal ba mtshungs par snang //
NK105(be)001:2852: de ltar 'gro drug 'jig rten drug po yang //
NK105(be)001:2853: las dang bag chags dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyis //
NK105(be)001:2854: bde sdug mtho dman rnam pa sna tshogs nyid //
NK105(be)001:2855: ston pa drug kyang 'gro sems rang snang ste //
NK105(be)001:2856: rmi lam nang gi sangs rgyas sems can bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2857: ngo bo dag kyang rnam pa ma dag pas //
NK105(be)001:2858: sna tshogs snang la thugs rje'i rol pa shar //
NK105(be)001:2859: 'di ni tshad med thugs rje'i sprul pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2860: srid pa ji srid phrin las rgyun mi 'chad //
NK105(be)001:2861: de nyid ngang las sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK105(be)001:2862: sems med bems po'i tshul gyis snang ba ste //
NK105(be)001:2863: ris su bris dang 'bur dang rang byon dang //
NK105(be)001:2864: yi ge la sogs mchod pa'i rten dang ni //
NK105(be)001:2865: pad+ma dpag bsam shing dang skyed mos tshal //
NK105(be)001:2866: khang bzangs mchog dang kun dag'i ra ba dang //
NK105(be)001:2867: sprul pa'i grong dang gru gzings zam pa dang //
NK105(be)001:2868: mar me nor bu zas gos bzhon pa sogs //
NK105(be)001:2869: 'gro ba'i don mang byed pa'i bems por snang //
NK105(be)001:2870: gnas skabs dga' skyid bde ba'i gnas mdzad nas //
NK105(be)001:2871: mthar thug zhi ba'i lam la 'god pas na //
NK105(be)001:2872: sna tshogs sprul pas 'gro don lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)001:2873: gdul bya med na 'dul byed dbyings su nub //
NK105(be)001:2874: rang snang longs sku chos sku'i ngang du thim //
NK105(be)001:2875: chu snod med na chu zla mkha' la thim //
NK105(be)001:2876: tshes kyi dbang gis zla ba dbyings su nub //
NK105(be)001:2877: gnam gang zla ba 'phel 'grib med pa bzhin //
NK105(be)001:2878: gdul bya yod na sngon bzhin rim gyis snang //
NK105(be)001:2879: 'di ni 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK105(be)001:2880: de ltar zhi ba mchog gi rang bzhin gyis //
NK105(be)001:2881: 'gro kun sems nyid 'od gsal dbyings gzhol te //
NK105(be)001:2882: srid zhi'i mthar 'dzin nyes cha'i dri ma yis //
NK105(be)001:2883: dub pa'i sems nyid de ring ngal sos shig /
NK105(be)001:2884: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK105(be)001:2885: 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o////de ltar legs bshad bsod nams sprin chen las //
NK105(be)001:2886: zhi bde'i rang bzhin char gyi tshogs mang pos //
NK105(be)001:2887: sa gsum 'gro ba'i dge legs rab rgyas te //
NK105(be)001:2888: rgyal ba'i 'byor tshogs lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK105(be)001:2889: ding sang phal gyi blo mig ma dag pas //
NK105(be)001:2890: sngags dang pha rol phyin gzhung so so'i lam //
NK105(be)001:2891: 'gal bar 'dzin pas gcig tu sdud mi shes //
NK105(be)001:2892: de phyir de dag phyogs re'i mig can yin //
NK105(be)001:2893: 'dir ni rgyu 'bras theg pa'i zab don mchog /
NK105(be)001:2894: gcig tu bsdus nas nyams su len pa'i thabs //
NK105(be)001:2895: gangs ri thod dkar o rgyan rdzong gnas su //
NK105(be)001:2896: dri med 'od zer shar bas legs par bkod //
NK105(be)001:2897: dge ba de yis srid pa'i sems can rnams //
NK105(be)001:2898: ma lus nyer zhi'i go 'phang mchog thob nas //
NK105(be)001:2899: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa yis //
NK105(be)001:2900: phyogs dus kun du bkra shis byed par shog //
NK105(be)001:2901: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso zhes bya ba /
NK105(be)001:2902: dpal o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po blo ldan
NK105(be)001:2903: mchog sred kyis rjes su bzung ba'i rnal 'byor pa
NK105(be)001:2904: dri med 'od zer gyis gangs ri thod dkar gyi
NK105(be)001:2905: mgul du legs par sbyar ba rdzogs so //
